%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-employees%20at%20Taser-making%20company%20felt%20pressured%20to%20get%20tattooed%20or%20shocked%20in%20front%20of%20crowds%2C%20report%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20barbed%20wires%20of%20Taser.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642c50d6fcb86b00180319c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20company%20Axon%20is%20known%20for%20its%20Tasers%2C%20a%20weapon%20designed%20to%20cause%20temporary%20paralysis.%20%3Cp%3ETHOMAS%20COEX%20%2F%20Contributor%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EReuters%20investigated%20the%20culture%20at%20Axon%2C%20the%20company%20that%20makes%20Tasers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFormer%20workers%20told%20the%20publication%20they%C2%A0felt%20pressured%20to%20get%20tattooed%20or%20shocked%20with%20Tasers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAxon%20denied%20that%20employees%20were%20pressured%20to%20engage%20in%20activities%20against%20their%20will.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20employees%20at%20the%20company%20that%20makes%20Tasers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Faxon-taser-exposures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20felt%20pressured%20to%20get%20tattooed%20or%20shocked%20with%20Tasers%20while%20working%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftaser-clues-fahim-saleh-murder-beheading-stolen-lipinski-stradivarius-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAxon%20Enterprise%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20Arizona%20company%20known%20for%20creating%20the%20Taser%2C%20a%20stun%20gun%20that%20fires%20barbs%20meant%20to%20cause%20temporary%20paralysis.%20Tasers%20are%20widely%20used%20by%20law-enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20staffers%20told%20Reuters%20that%20the%20company%20had%20an%20all-in%2C%20high-pressure%20culture%20of%20loyalty%20that%20led%20to%20some%20staffers%20feeling%20pushed%20to%20be%20publicly%20shocked%20by%20Tasers%20in%20demonstrations%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bexposures.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAxon%20denied%20that%20staffers%20were%20pressured%20to%20engage%20in%20the%20exposures.%20In%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider%2C%20the%20company%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20strongly%20object%20to%20any%20implication%20that%20Axon%20pressures%20employees%20to%20engage%20in%20activities%20against%20their%20will.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20shared%20with%20Reuters%2C%20Axon%20CEO%20Rick%20Smith%20said%20being%20stunned%20by%20a%20Taser%20was%20%26quot%3Bunpleasant%26quot%3B%C2%A0but%20defended%20the%20exposures%20by%20comparing%20them%20to%20law-enforcement%20practices.%20He%20said%20most%20of%20Axon's%20law-enforcement%20customers%20offered%20officer%20demos%20as%20a%20way%20to%20develop%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeeper%20understanding%20of%20the%20technology%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20empathy%20for%20people%20on%20the%20receiving%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20investigation%2C%20Reuters%20reviewed%20internal%20Axon%20records%2C%20including%20announcements%2C%20meeting%20notes%2C%20and%2024%20videos%20of%20staff%20members%20being%20shocked%20with%20Tasers.%20The%20agency%20also%20interviewed%2063%20current%20and%20former%20employees%2C%20including%20nine%20former%20executives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReuters%20said%20several%20former%20employees%20compared%20the%20company%20exposures%20to%20a%20scene%20reminiscent%20of%20ancient%20Rome's%20Colosseum%2C%20including%20a%20former%20international%20support%20manager%20who%20said%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Blike%20a%20scene%20from%20ancient%20Rome%2C%20gladiator-style.%26quot%3B%20That%20person%20added%20there%20was%20general%20pressure%20for%20staff%20members%20to%20be%20shot%20with%20Tasers%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20ex-staffers%20told%20Reuters%20that%20some%20Axon%20executives%20encouraged%20other%20employees%20to%20get%20company-themed%20tattoos.%20The%20company%20even%20brought%20tattoo%20artists%20to%20internal%20conferences%20this%20year%20and%20the%20last%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20execs%20who%20got%20tattoos%20were%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20ones%20who%20were%20all%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20former%20employees%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%20being%20branded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Axon%20representative%20told%20Insider%20there%20was%20no%20pressure%20for%20staff%20members%20to%20participate%20in%20%26quot%3Bexposures%20or%20obtaining%20an%20Axon%20tattoo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20make%20significant%20effort%20to%20ensure%20people%20understand%20it's%20not%20expected%20of%20them%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20if%20they%20choose%20to%20participate%2C%20they%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20safety%20considerations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20continued.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20our%20board%20and%20many%20of%20our%20most%20senior%20executives%20have%20chosen%20not%20to%20experience%20Taser%20exposures%20and%20we%20estimate%20that%20about%2099.5%25%20of%20our%20staff%20do%20not%20have%20Axon-related%20tattoos.%20It%20has%20never%20impeded%20anyone's%20career%20advancement%2C%20and%20it%20has%20never%20even%20come%20up%20as%20a%20topic%20in%20any%20reviews%20for%20hiring%20or%20promotion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faxon-taser-staff-pressured-staff-get-tattooed-shocked-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694010300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f84d1904e14000196c9d6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faxon-taser-staff-pressured-staff-get-tattooed-shocked-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20a%20Reuters%20investigation%2C%20ex-staffers%20described%20the%20com