9517.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eengaged%20in%20an%20aggressive%20on-field%20spat%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20versus%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20match%20in%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discernible%20%E2%80%98Kohli%2C%20Kohli%E2%80%99%20chant%20which%20triggered%20the%20strong%20response%20from%20Gambhir%20in%20Pallekele%20can%20be%20heard%20in%20clips%20being%20circulated%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Gambhir%20later%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1698712472327446875%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20shown%20on%20social%20media%20has%20no%20truth%20in%20it%20because%20people%20show%20whatever%20they%20want%20to%20show.%20The%20truth%20about%20the%20video%20that%20went%20viral%20is%20that%20if%20you%20raise%20anti-India%20slogans%20and%20speak%20about%20Kashmir%2C%20then%20the%20person%20before%20you%20will%20obviously%20react%20and%20not%20smile%20and%20leave.%20There%20were%20two%20to%20three%20Pakistanis%20there%20who%20were%20speaking%20anti-India%20things%20and%20things%20on%20Kashmir.%20So%2C%20it%20was%20my%20natural%20reaction.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20hear%20anything%20against%20my%20country.%20So%2C%20that%20was%20my%20reaction%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFact-check%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20found%20that%20the%20video%20clips%20with%20the%20chant%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CBharat%20Tere%20Tukde%20Honge%2C%20Inshallah%20Inshallah%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20doctored.%20The%20slogan%20has%20been%20edited%20into%20the%20video%20of%20Gambhir%20flashing%20his%20middle%20finger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20readers%20should%20note%20that%20some%20of%20the%20viral%20videos%20have%20the%20text%20%E2%80%98xTripti%E2%80%99%20imposed%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20discovered%20that%20Twitter%20user%20%40xTripti%20was%20the%20creator%20of%20the%20viral%20video%20with%20the%20anti-India%20slogans%2C%20who%20has%20now%20deleted%20their%20account.%20However%2C%20before%20the%20deletion%2C%20they%20clarified%20in%20several%20tweets%20that%20the%20video%20has%20been%20edited.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2FqYra2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2Fm928O%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2FWK1j1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20the%20archives%20of%20those%20tweets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audio%20(the%20anti-India%20sloganeering)%20has%20been%20taken%20from%20widely%20circulated%20videos%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fdidnt-your-blood-boil-stories-from-the-churning-of-indias-youth%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%2598Bharat%2520tere%2520tukde%2520honge%25E2%2580%25A6Insha%2520Allah.%2520Insha%2520Allah%252C%25E2%2580%2599%2520the%2520policeman%25E2%2580%2599s%2520cell%2520phone%2520played%2520visuals%2520of%2520a%2520group%2520shouting%2520the%2520slogan.%2520%25E2%2580%2598Can%2520you%2520hear%2520this%253F%25E2%2580%2599%2520the%2520interrogating%2520cop%2520asked.%250AUmar%2520Khalid%2520nodded%252C%2520%25E2%2580%2598That%25E2%2580%2599s%2520only%2520two%2520minutes%2520of%2520a%2520two%252Dhour%252Dlong%2520programme.%25E2%2580%2599%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20event%20called%20%E2%80%98The%20country%20without%20a%20post%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20organised%20at%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20on%20February%209%2C%202016%2C%20where%20anti-India%20slogans%20were%20allegedly%20raised.%20The%20programme%2C%20which%20was%20orga