20NYU%2C%20I%20tried%20my%20best%20to%20take%20it%20all%20in.%20This%20was%20a%20huge%20day%20for%20me%2C%20likely%20one%20I%20would%20remember%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20lugging%20everything%20out%20of%20the%20car%20and%20into%20my%20building's%20elevator%2C%20I%20finally%20arrived%20at%20my%20dorm%2C%20which%20is%20a%20triple.%20There%2C%20I%20met%20one%20of%20my%20roommates%2C%20along%20with%20her%20family.%20It%20was%20bizarre%20to%20meet%20someone%20for%20the%20first%20time%20while%20knowing%20I'd%20be%20sharing%20a%20room%20with%20them%20for%20the%20next%20nine%20months.%20But%20it%20was%20comforting%20to%20have%20connected%20with%20her%20before%20move-in%20day%20via%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20immediately%20drawn%20to%20the%20floor-to-ceiling%20windows%20as%20natural%20light%20lit%20up%20the%20space.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20I%20noticed%20the%20Empire%20State%20Building%20peeking%20through%20the%20skyline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReality%20began%20to%20set%20in%3A%20New%20York%20was%20a%20place%20that%20I'd%20once%20thought%20of%20as%20a%20distant%20dream%2C%20but%20now%20it%20was%20my%20new%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20to%20unpack%20my%20belongings%20%E2%80%94%20and%20started%20my%20new%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20two%20hours%2C%20I%20had%20the%20very%20stressful%20task%20of%20setting%20up%20my%20new%20home.%20When%20my%20second%20roommate%20arrived%2C%20we%20each%20started%20to%20unpack%2C%20unraveling%20layers%20of%20packing%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20overwhelmed%20and%20unsure%20of%20where%20to%20start%20as%20I%20looked%20at%20all%20my%20belongings%20spread%20out%20on%20the%20floor.%20As%20someone%20who's%20particular%20about%20the%20organization%20of%20her%20living%20space%2C%20I%20found%20it%20mentally%20taxing%20to%20artfully%20arrange%20my%20new%20room%20within%20a%20matter%20of%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20Zoe%20Applebaum's%20nyu%20dorm%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f789671b7ced0019c8864c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20finalized%20dorm.%3Cp%3E%20Zoe%20Applebaum%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20finally%20done%2C%20I%20realized%20my%20dorm%20space%20wasn't%20perfect.%20I%20had%20to%20remind%20myself%20at%20that%20moment%20that%20good%20was%20good%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20roommates%20and%20I%20then%20decided%20to%20grab%20lunch%20somewhere%20around%20campus%20before%20heading%20to%20Target%20to%20get%20a%20few%20things.%20The%20number%20of%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%20lunch%20spots%2C%20and%20grab-and-go%20food%20options%20around%20Greenwich%20Village%20seemed%20endless.%20Some%20places%20even%20offer%20an%20NYU-student%20discount%2C%20which%20I%20took%20note%20of%20for%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20orientation%20didn't%20start%20until%20the%20following%20Monday%2C%20I%20had%20some%20time%20to%20explore.%20I%20acquainted%20myself%20with%20some%20of%20the%20other%20students%20living%20in%20my%20dorm.%20I%20also%20explored%20the%20city%20with%20my%20roommates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20not%20prepared%20for%20the%20amount%20of%20walking%20I%20would%20do.%20My%20health%20app's%20step%20count%20skyrocketed%20to%20well%20over%2010%2C000%20steps%2C%20and%20I%20could%20feel%20my%20heels%20digging%20into%20the%20soles%20of%20my%20shoes%20every%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20realized%20New%20York%20City%20would%20be%20an%20adjustment%20for%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20first%20few%20days%20at%20NYU%2C%20I%20found%20the%20city%20overstimulating.%20There%20were%20loud%20noises%2C%20cars%20racing%20by%2C%20and%20large%20groups%20of%20people%20surrounding%20me%20at%20every%20turn.%20While%20I%20considered%20myself%20a%20citygoer%20and%20someone%20who%20generally%20liked%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%20of%20a%20big%2