l%20Wahlstr%C3%B6m.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20creating%20the%20issue%2C%20Wahlstr%C3%B6m%20discovered%20AI%20can%20have%20a%20stereotypical%20vision%20of%20women.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI%20images%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bwarning%20flag%26quot%3B%20to%20stop%20looking%20back%20and%20move%20forward%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20images%20within%20the%20inaugural%20issue%20of%20Copy%20magazine%20are%20eerily%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EModels%20stare%20at%20the%20viewer%20with%20sharp%2C%20rosy%20cheekbones%20and%20soft%2C%20tousled%20hair.%20Their%20blemish-free%20skin%20glows%20where%20the%20light%20hits%20and%20their%20lips%20are%20either%20pursed%20in%20a%20sultry%20pout%20or%20opened%20to%20reveal%20a%20radiant%20smile%20of%20straight%20teeth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20none%20of%20these%20models%20are%20real%20people%20%E2%80%94%20every%20photo%2C%20and%20even%20the%20text%2C%20is%20AI-generated.%20The%20brainchild%20of%20a%20Swedish%20advertising%20consultant%2C%20Copy%20was%20meant%20to%20blur%20the%20lines%20between%20reality%20and%20fantasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22an%20AI-generated%20photo%20of%20a%20model%20walking%20down%20a%20runway%20in%20a%20brown%20dress%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f24a417819260019104547%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20spreads%20in%20Copy%20magazine%20places%20AI-generated%20models%20on%20the%20runway%20at%20fashion%20week.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Copy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20stereotypical%20depiction%20of%20beauty%20was%20on%20purpose%2C%20creator%20Carl-Axel%20Wahlstr%C3%B6m%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20argue%20that%20all%20the%20women%20in%20the%20pictures%20are%20very%20stereotyped%20and%20perfect%2C%20but%20that%20was%20also%20a%20concept%20to%20show%20everybody%20that%20this%20is%20the%20image%20of%20beauty%20that%20we%20have%20been%20fed%20with%20through%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%20years%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20struggling%20a%20lot%20with%20it%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20everything%20that%20I%20prompt%2C%20even%20though%20I%20write%20the%20opposite%2C%20it%20just%20becomes%20too%20perfect%20and%20too%20beautiful%20and%20too%20stereotyped%3F%20But%20I%20think%20that%20it%20was%20an%20important%20thing%20to%20also%20show%20that%20this%20is%20how%20we%20have%20seen%20beauty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20inaugural%20issue%20launched%20in%20August.%20Wahlstr%C3%B6m%20said%20he%20thought%20of%20the%20idea%20for%20the%20magazine%20in%20March%2C%20when%20the%20AI%20software%20company%20Midjourney%20released%20a%20new%20version%20of%20its%20text-to-image%20technology%20with%20photorealism%20capabilities.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20blown%20away%20and%20in%20love%20with%20the%20whole%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22an%20AI-generated%20photo%20of%20a%20woman%20wearing%20a%20race%20car%20helmet%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f24ab67819260019104606%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221429%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnother%20spread%20in%20Copy%20magazine%20portrayed%20AI-generated%20female%20race-car%20drivers.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Copy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20each%20image%20was%20initially%20AI-generated%20from%20text%20prompts%2C%20Wahlstr%C3%B6m%20said%20he%20and%20his%20team%20retouched%20every%20picture%2C%20a%20process%20that%20could%20take%2010%20hours%20per%20photo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20fashion%20photography%20in%20general%2C%20you%20take%20a%20picture%20of%20someone%20and%20you%20make%20it%20more%20perfect%20than%20it%20actually%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20AI%20prompting%20and%20image%20making%2C%20we%20try%20to%20take%20the%20perfect%20AI%20image%20and%20deconstruct%20it%20so%20that%20it's%20not%20that%20perfect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20photographs%20are%20dreamlike%20in%20their%20blurred%20edges%2C%20crisp%20details%2C%20and%20saturated%20colors.%20The%20editorials%20follow%20women%20as%20Formula%20One%20drivers%2C%20brokers%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20and%20models%20at%20fashion%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20enhance%20the%20role%20of%20women%20in%20society%20in%20a%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Wahlstr%C3%B6m%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%20there%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20criticism%20towards%20the%20fashion%20industry%20and%20to%20how%20we%20are%20portraying%20women.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20technology%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20images%20and%20information%20we%20give%20it%2C%20he%20said.%20So%20it%20made%20sense%20that%20when%20asked%20to%20generate%20photos%20of%20women%2C%20the%20software%20would%20throw%20back%20a%20culmination%20of%20all%20the%20stereotypes%20we've%20collected%20on%20the%20internet%20since%201983.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20doesn't%20come%20up%20with%20anything%20new%2C%20it%20just%20summarizes%20the%20whole%20bulk%20of%20images%20that%20we%20have%20uploaded%20to%20the%20internet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20partly%20AI-generated%20photo%20of%20a%20man%20wearing%20period%20clothing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f24bae1b7ced0019c725ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222828%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20his%20headshot%2C%20Carl-Axel%20Wahlstr%C3%B6m%2C%20added%20his%20face%20to%20an%20AI-generated%20body%20wearing%20period%20clothing.%20%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Carl-Axel%20Wahlstr%C3%B6m%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Wahlstr%C3%B6m%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20define%20fashion%20of%20the%20last%20two%20decades%20without%20the%20AI%20referring%20back%20to%20styles%20from%20previous%20decades%20like%20the%20'80s%20and%20'90s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20looping%20these%20decades%20over%20and%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%20and%20that%20made%20the%20AI%20very%20confused%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20says%20a%20lot%20about%20us%2C%20and%20I%20think%20this%20is%20really%20a%20warning%20flag%20to%20stop%20repeating%2C%20stop%20looking%20back%2C%20and%20try%20to%20move%20forward%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fashion%20and%20advertising%20industries%20have%20been%20slow%20to%20embrace%20AI%20photography.%20As%20a%20consultant%20to%20major%20apparel%20brands%20like%20H%26amp%3BM%20and%20Gant%2C%20Wahlstr%C3%B6m%20said%20he's%20talked%20with%20companies%20that%20are%20interested%2C%20but%20hesitant%20to%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdvertisers%20are%20a%20little%20bit%20afraid%20of%20what%20their%20audience%20will%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20many%20brands%2C%20it's%20very%20important%20to%20be%20on%20the%20right%20side.%20No%20one%20really%20knows%20how%20AI%20will%20be%20seen.%20Is%20this%20a%20threat%20to%20humanity%3F%20As%20many%20people%20are%20saying.%20Is%20it%20fair%20to%20combine%20a%20real%20product%20that%20should%20symbolize%20quality%20with%20pictures%20that%20are%20not%20real%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22an%20AI-generated%20image%20of%20a%20woman's%20face%20and%20her%20hair%20cascading%20around%20her%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f24c207819260019104814%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAll%20of%20the%20models%20in%20Copy%20magazine%20were%20AI-generated.%20%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Copy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20of%20AI%20can%20even%20worry%20Wahlstr%C3%B6m%20at%20times.%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20I%20get%20a%20little%20bit%20stressed%20by%20the%20whole%20technology%2C%20%3Cspan%3Eand%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eit's%3Cspan%3E%20moving%20so%20fast%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20But%20he%20believes%20there%20are%20also%20many%20ways%20the%20industry%20could%20benefit%20from%20AI%20photography.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20democratize%20who%20actually%20can%20make%20a%20really%20great%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20people%20will%20always%20take%20pictures.%20I%20think%20the%20AI%20technology%20is%20more%20just%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20another%20type%20of%20camera%2C%20not%20a%20replacement%20for%20the%20camera.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECopy%20is%20available%20to%20purchase%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapercutshop.se%2Fproduct%2Fcopy-issue-1%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eonline%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Wahlstr%C3%B6m%20plans%20to%20release%20the%20magazine%20twice%20a%20year%20and%20said%20the%20next%20issue%20could%20come%20out%20between%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%20and%20the%20beginning%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20process%20of%20making%20these%20magazines%20is%20so%20much%20fun%20and%20I'm%20learning%20so%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20really%20feels%20like%20you're%20sort%20of%20pioneering%20something%20new.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-fashion-magazine-copy-shows-women-stereotyped-perfect-images-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694008061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f24cf9781926001910498f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-fashion-magazine-copy-shows-women-stereotyped-perfect-images-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22None%20of%20the%20models%20in%20Copy%20magazine%20are%20real.%20Every%20photo%20and%20text%20is%20AI-generated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jortakales%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20