n%20called%20following%20tradition.%20Perhaps%20you%20are%20not%20paying%20attention%20to%20tradition.%20Before%20calling%20the%20Parliament%20session%2C%20there%20is%20never%20any%20discussion%20with%20political%20parties%2C%20nor%20are%20the%20issues%20discussed.%20After%20the%20calling%20of%20the%20session%20by%20the%20President%20and%20before%20commencement%20of%20the%20session%2C%20there%20is%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20leaders%20of%20all%20the%20parties%20in%20which%20the%20people%20rising%20in%20the%20Parliament%20are%20discussed.%20Issues%20and%20work%20are%20discussed.%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspense%20over%20the%20agenda%20has%20triggered%20speculation%20on%20the%20country's%20name%20change.%20The%20trigger%20was%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu's%20invite%20to%20G20%20leaders%20where%20she%20has%20been%20described%20as%20%26quot%3BPresident%20of%20Bharat%26quot%3B.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20a%20document%20surfaced%20that%20saw%20PM%20Modi%20being%20described%20a%20%26quot%3BPrime%20Minister%20of%20Bharat%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20a%20post%20on%20X%20went%20viral%20that%20said%20Pakistan%20may%20lay%20claim%20to%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20may%20lay%20claim%20to%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20if%20India%20derecongnises%20it%20officially%20at%20UN%20level.%20--local%20media.%20Nationalists%20in%20Pakistan%20have%20long%20argued%20that%20Pakistan%20has%20rights%20to%20the%20name%20as%20it%20refers%20to%20the%20Indus%20region%20in%20Pakistan%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20post%20shared%20by%20South%20Asia%20Index's%20X%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20sources%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20G-20%20summit%2C%20to%20be%20held%20this%20weekend%2C%20will%20be%20the%20subject%20of%20the%20special%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694007120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fiuoha618_sonia-gandhi-ani-1200_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fminister-responds-to-sonia-gandhis-letter-to-pm-says-parties-never-consulted-before-calling-parliament-session-4365439%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Congress%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20nine-point%20letter%20on%20the%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20has%20drawn%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fminister-responds-to-sonia-gandhis-letter-to-pm-says-parties-never-consulted-before-calling-parliament-session-4365439%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fminister-responds-to-sonia-gandhis-letter-to-pm-says-parties-never-consulted-before-calling-parliament-session-4365439%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fminister-responds-to-sonia-gandhis-letter-to-pm-says-parties-never-consulted-before-calling-parliament-session-4365439%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Asian%20Activists%20Object%20to%20India%20Hosting%20Conference%20of%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Institutions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F22164136%2Fimage-859.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20South%20Asian%20group%20of%20human%20rights%20activists%20has%20objected%20to%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20Forum%20of%20regional%20national%20human%20rights%20institutions%20holding%20its%20next%20meeting%20in%20India%20due%20to%20the%20failure%20of%20NHRC%20to%20meet%20its%20mandated%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsouthasianrights.org%2F2023%2F09%2F04%2Fsahr-is-outraged-to-learn-that-apf-has-allowed-the-indian-nhric-to-host-it-next-conference%2F%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Colombo-based%20South%20Asians%20for%20Human%20Rights%20(SAHR)%2C%20a%20democratic%20regional%20body%2C%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Coutraged%20to%20learn%20that%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20Forum%20has%20allowed%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20of%20India%20(NHRC)%20to%20host%20its%20next%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%2020%20and%2021%20September%2C%202023%E2%80%9D.%20The%20group%20added%20that%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20Forum%20has%20announced%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20inaugurate%20the%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20behalf%20of%20the%20civil%20society%20members%20of%20the%20South%20Asian%20region%20committed%20to%20the%20promotion%20and%20protection%20of%20human%20rights%20at%20the%20national%20and%20regional%20level%2C%20SAHR%20perceives%20that%20this%20decision%20of%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20Forum%20will%20defeat%20the%20purpose%20as%20well%20as%20the%20past%20and%20future%20achievements%20it%20has%20so%20far%20been%20working%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20Asian%20group%20pointed%20out%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20NHRC%20has%20still%20been%20accredited%20with%20an%20%E2%80%98A%E2%80%99%20grade%20status%20till%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20highlighted%20that%20the%20sub-committee%20on%20accreditation%20(SCA)%20of%20the%20Global%20Alliance%20of%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Institutions%20(GANHRI)%20had%20recommended%20in%20March%20this%20year%20that%20further%20consideration%20on%20its%20accreditation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fun-affiliated-agency-defers-accreditation-nhrc-human-rights-8628157%2F%5C%22%3Ewill%20be%20deferred%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20giving%20its%20recommendation%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fganhri.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2FSCA-Report-First-Session-2023-EN.pdf%5C%22%3Esub-committee%20had%20objected%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20legislation%20governing%20the%20NHRC%20that%20allowed%20for%20police%20officers%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20investigation%20of%20cases.%20This%20objection%20to%20provisions%20of%20the%20Protection%20of%20Human%20Rights%20Act%20of%201993%20had%20been%20raised%20as%20far%20back%20as%202017%2C%20but%20was%20not%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SCA%20reiterates%20that%20a%20fundamental%20requirement%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Finstruments-mechanisms%2Finstruments%2Fprinciples-relating-status-national-institutions-paris%5C%22%3EParis%20Principles%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20an%20NHRI%20is%2C%20and%20is%20perceived%20to%20be%2C%20able%20to%20operate%20independent%20of%20government%20interference.%20Where%20an%20NHRI%E2%80%99s%20members%20are%20seconded%20from%20the%20public%20service%2C%20and%20in%20particular%20where%20this%20includes%20those%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20in%20the%20NHRI%2C%20it%20raises%20questions%20about%20its%20capacity%20to%20fully%20function%20independently%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fnhrcs-international-accreditation-deferred-no-one-batting-with-a-straight-bat%2F%5C%22%3E%20SCA%20report%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20report%20had%20also%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20plurality%20of%20the%20membership%2C%20selection%20and%20appointment%20of%20members%2C%20appointment%20of%20secretary%20general%20and%20cooperation%20with%20other%20human%20rights%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCA%20had%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20NHRC%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20provide%20sufficient%20information%20with%20regards%20to%20how%20it%20implements%20its%20full%20mandate%20to%20monitor%2C%20promote%2C%20and%20protect%20the%20rights%20of%20everyone%20including%20religious%20minorities%20and%20HRDs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20SAHR%20statement%20alleged%20that%20the%20NHRC%20had%20%E2%80%9Cfailed%20to%20do%20mandated%20duties%20as%20an%20independent%20institution%20ad