0Democrats%E2%80%99%20presidential%20candidate%2C%20Iliyas%20Labeeb%20had%20to%20carefully%20navigate%20on%20this%20path%2C%20stating%20that%20any%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20presence%E2%80%9D%20should%20be%20transparent%20and%20that%20no%20country%20should%20influence%20Maldives%20at%20the%20debate.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fatolltimes.mv%2Fpost%2Fnews%2F4789%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20interview%20on%20July%2027%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20he%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20gauge%20how%20much%20Indian%20influence%20there%20was%20in%20Maldives%2C%20but%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%20have%20concerns%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F18113525%2FModi-Solih.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F18113525%2FModi-Solih.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F18113525%2FModi-Solih-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F18113525%2FModi-Solih-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-312165%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFILE%20IMAGE.%20Maldives%20president%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih%20greeting%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20Maldives%20government%20website%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Democrats%20split%20away%20from%20the%20ruling%20MDP%2C%20after%20former%20President%20Mohamed%20Nasheed%20had%20failed%20to%20win%20the%20primary%20to%20be%20the%20party%20presidential%20candidate.%20Nasheed%20had%20always%20been%20a%20champion%20of%20strong%20ties%20with%20India%2C%20but%20his%20newly-formed%20party%20has%20seemingly%20made%20calculations%20on%20its%20political%20positioning%20in%20order%20to%20remain%20electorally%20relevant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20three%20independent%20candidates%2C%20Hassan%20Zameel%2C%20who%20resigned%20as%20deputy%20defence%20minister%20recently%20to%20stand%20for%20elections%2C%20was%20less%20strident%20on%20relations%20with%20India%20during%20the%20debate.%20He%20asserted%20that%20had%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20observed%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20operating%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20threatens%20Maldivians%2C%20and%20that%20there%20is%20no%20danger%20to%20national%20security%20from%20their%20presence%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20expected%2C%20Miuzzi%2C%20the%20primary%20opposition%20candidate%2C%20restated%20his%20criticism%20on%20Solih%E2%80%99s%20ties%20with%20India%20at%20the%20televised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%2C%20a%20few%20days%20later%2C%20he%20went%20further%20and%20asserted%20that%20suggesting%20that%20Indian-backed%20initiatives%20could%20be%20at%20risk%20of%20termination%20if%20he%20were%20to%20win%20the%20elections.%20He%20pointed%20to%20the%20cancelled%20GMR%20airport%20project%20as%20an%20example.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20not%20only%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20Uthuru%20development%20but%20also%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20delays%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Mal%C3%A9-Thilafushi%20link%20bridge%2C%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20biggest%20infrastructure%20project%20that%20is%20being%20executed%20by%20Indian%20firms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDefending%20himself%2C%20Solih%20argued%20that%20foreign%20troops%20in%20Maldives%20were%20only%20stationed%20for%20training%20activities%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Favas.mv%2Fen%2F135180%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edid%20not%20carry%20out%20any%20military%20operations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20no%20foreign%20troops%20in%20this%20country%20today%20for%20military%20operations%E2%80%94neither%20yesterday%20nor%20before%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20stressed%20that%20these%20training%20programs%20included%20not%20just%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20but%20also%20military%20personnel%20from%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAhead%20of%20the%20polls%2C%20Solih%20has%20also%20been%20on%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsmnews.mv%2Fen%2F125785%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espree%20inaugurating%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsmnews.mv%2Fen%2F125439%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einfrastructure%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20projects%20in%20various%20outlying%20atolls.%20Among%20them%20were%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHCIMaldives%2Fstatus%2F1696812319186255901%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprojects%20completed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20line%20of%20credit.%20Maldivian%20foreign%20minister%20also%20announced%20on%20Aug%2031%20that%20India%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fabdulla_shahid%2Fstatus%2F1697258860837556506%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eapproved%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20three%20new%20projects%20under%20the%20High%20Impact%20Community%20Development%20Project%20grant%20scheme.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20relations%20with%20Maldives%20had%20certainly%20rebounded%20from%20its%20nadir%20under%20China-aligned%20Yameen%20government%20after%20Solih%20won%20the%202018%20elections%20in%20a%20landslide%20win.%20It%20meant%20India%20had%20been%20generous%20in%20announcing%20a%20slew%20of%20development%20projects%20and%20invested%20considerable%20diplomatic%20capital.%20Therefore%2C%20a%20Solih%20victory%20would%20certainly%20assure%20New%20Delhi%20that%20relations%20with%20the%20strategically-placed%20Indian%20ocean%20island%20nation%20will%20be%20on%20an%20even%20keel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%2C%20it%20is%20not%20an%20easy%20path%20for%20the%20incumbent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmaldives-explainer-presidential-election-ibrahim-solih%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20written%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20campaign%20period%2C%20the%20long%20line-up%20of%20candidates%20suggests%20that%20voting%20will%20be%20fragmented%2C%20making%20it%20unlikely%20for%20any%20candidate%20to%20secure%20an%20outright%20victory%20in%20the%20first%20round%20by%20surpassing%20the%20halfway%20mark.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%2042%25%20of%20voters%20in%20Maldives%20have%20not%20registered%20themselves%20as%20members%20of%20any%20political%20party.%20As%20per%20norm%2C%20they%20will%20determine%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20candidates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EObservers%20estimate%20that%20around%2020%20to%2030%25%20of%20voters%20are%20still%20estimated.%20According%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbaanicentre.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FCombined-August-Report.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epoll%20conducted%20in%20August%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20number%20of%20undecided%20could%20be%20as%20high%20at%2052%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Solih%20and%20Muizzu%20would%20win%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20votes%2C%20there%20is%20toss-up%20between%20Ilyas%20and%20Qasim%20on%20who%20will%20come%20third.%20It%20is%20reported%20that%20the%20crowds%20at%20The%20Democrats%E2%80%99%20rallies%20have%20been%20substantial%2C%20while%20Gasim%20has%20a%20captive%20votebank%20from%20his%20thousands%20of%20resort%20employees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20no%20one%20wins%2050%25%20of%20the%20votes%2C%20the%20top%20two%20candidates%20will%20have%20to%20go%20for%20a%20run-off%20within%2021%20days%20as%20per%20constitutional%20guidelines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20performance%20of%20the%20leading%20two%20candidates%20in%20the%20first%20round%20is%20pivotal%20for%20forging%20alliances%20with%20the%20defeated%20parties%20and%20candidates%2C%20whose%20support%20will%20be%20crucial%20in%20securing%20victory%20in%20the%20runoff.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Machiavellian%20manoeuvring%20in%20Maldivian%20politics%20typically%20kicks%20into%20gear%20after%20the%20first%20round%20results%20are%20known%2C%20as%20politicians%20and%20their%20supporters%20choose%20between%20two%20camps%20based%20on%20who%20poses%20the%20least%20significant%20threats%20to%20their%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694006130000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06184333%2FF5VkbOhawAAlNKm.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia-ibrahim-solih-maldives-presidential-election%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Machiavellian%20manoeuvring%20in%20Maldivian%20politics%20typically%20kicks%20into%20gear%20after%20the%20first%20round%20results%20are%20known%2C%20as%20politicians%20and%20their%20supporters%20choose%20between%20two%20camps%20based%20on%20who%20poses%20the%20least%20significant%20threats%20to%20their%20interests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia-ibrahim-solih-maldives-presidential-election%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Bharat%20or%20India%3F%E2%80%99%3A%20SC%20Had%20Said%20in%202016%20That%20Citizens%20Are%20Free%20to%20Use%20Either%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F20