m%20a%20floor%20mop%20sink%20with%20orange%20juice.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Tianye%20Restaurant%2C%20a%20popular%20chain%20in%20eastern%20China%2C%20has%20since%20apologised%20after%20facing%20widespread%20backlash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20hygiene%20scandal%20erupted%20when%20a%20customer%20at%20the%20restaurant%20discreetly%20recorded%20an%20employee%20placing%20a%20large%20pot%20of%20concentrated%20orange%20juice%20into%20a%20basin%20used%20for%20washing%20mops%20and%20adding%20tap%20water.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Ftrending-china%2Farticle%2F3233131%2Ffelt-sick-my-stomach-restaurant-china-caught-mixing-orange-juice-tap-water-mop-sink-apologises-and%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20the%20clip%2C%20mops%20and%20brooms%20were%20also%20seen%20hanging%20next%20to%20the%20basin%2C%20and%20a%20dustpan%20filled%20with%20rubbish%20added%20to%20the%20unsettling%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation%20became%20evident%20when%20the%20employee%20noticed%20the%20customer%20filming%20her%20and%20hastily%20transferred%20the%20juice%20mixture%20into%20a%20serving%20pot.%20Other%20staff%20members%20attempted%20to%20prevent%20the%20filming%2C%20but%20the%20damage%20had%20already%20been%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20just%20use%20tap%20water%20to%20make%20orange%20juice%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20man%20shouted%20to%20other%20diners%20in%20the%20video.%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20letting%20so%20many%20customers%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fseems-disrespectful-spanish-influencer-faces-backlash-for-swimming-in-banned-canary-islands-cave-4364025%5C%22%3ESpanish%20Influencer%20Faces%20Backlash%20For%20Swimming%20In%20Banned%20Canary%20Islands%20Cave%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20particularly%20struck%20a%20chord%20in%20Wenzhou%2C%20where%20the%20free%20orange%20juice%20is%20popular%20with%20children%20and%20teenagers.%20Taking%20to%20social%20media%2C%20residents%20expressed%20their%20anger%20and%20demanded%20accountability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Tianye%20Restaurant%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20August%2026.%20It%20apologised%20for%20the%20incident%20and%20blamed%20it%20on%20a%20lack%20of%20supervision%20and%20a%20relaxed%20management%20style%20at%20the%20chain%20eatery%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20the%20restaurant%20also%20informed%20that%20it%20has%20demoted%20the%20restaurant's%20manager%20and%20suspended%20the%20employees%20involved.%20The%20eatery%20also%20enrolled%20the%20accused%20staff%20in%20a%20comprehensive%20food%20hygiene%20training%20program.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Chinese%20social%20media%20erupted%20with%20one%20user%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20vicious%20and%20disgusting!%20It%20deserves%20fierce%20condemnation%26quot%3B.%20Others%20also%20highlighted%20the%20need%20for%20stricter%20penalties%20to%20deter%20such%20food%20safety%20violations.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20committing%20this%20crime%20is%20low%20and%20the%20punishment%20is%20too%20light%20are%20the%20reasons%20for%20myriad%20food%20safety%20scandal%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694003940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F6dbi8dmg_oj-rep_625x300_06_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-restaurant-sparks-outrage-after-staff-caught-mixing-orange-juice-with-mop-sink-water-4365474%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20restaurant%20in%20China%20has%20sparked%20outrage%20online%20after%20an%20employee%20was%20caught%20on%20camera%20mixing%20tap%20water%20from%20a%20floor%20mop%20sink%20with%20orange%20juice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-restaurant-sparks-outrage-after-staff-caught-mixing-orange-juice-with-mop-sink-water-4365474%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-restaurant-sparks-outrage-after-staff-caught-mixing-orange-juice-with-mop-sink-water-4365474%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-restaurant-sparks-outrage-after-staff-caught-mixing-orange-juice-with-mop-sink-water-4365474%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G20%20Must%20Devise%20a%20Human%20SOP%20For%20When%20Foreign%20Services%20Remove%20Kids%20From%20Indian%20Families%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06180630%2FUntitled-design-4.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20diaspora%20at%2032%20million%2C%20with%20over%20a%20million%20of%20our%20citizens%20going%20abroad%20for%20work%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENotably%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20number%20of%20Indians%20relinquishing%20their%20citizenship%20is%20relatively%20low.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20renouncing%20their%20citizenship%20stood%20at%200.16%20million.%20This%20means%20that%20the%20connection%20with%20India%20of%20our%20migrant%20population%20remains%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20connection%20is%20not%20merely%20the%20legal%20one%20of%20citizenship.%20Personal%20foreign%20remittances%20to%20India%20are%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20world%20at%20US%20%24%2089%20billion%20according%20to%20figures%20for%202021.%20They%20are%20expected%20to%20rise%20to%20US%20%24%20100%20billion%20this%20year.%20This%20is%20money%20that%20Indians%20working%20abroad%20are%20sending%20back%20home%20to%20their%20families.%20The%20connection%20with%20the%20home%20country%2C%20is%20filial%20and%20emotional.%20Cultural%20attributes%20too%20remain%20intact%20even%20after%20decades%2C%20even%20generations%20away%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMigration%20is%20certainly%20no%20longer%20a%20one-way%20street.%20Significantly%2C%20in%20recent%20times%20migrant%20population%20of%20all%20backgrounds%20have%20chosen%20retirement%20in%20India%20even%20as%20some%20have%20chosen%20to%20permanently%20settle%20in%20the%20host%20countries.%20With%20rapid%20developments%20in%20the%20urban%20landscape%20of%20India%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20trend%20of%20highly-skilled%20professionals%2C%20graduates%20of%20our%20prestigious%20engineering%20and%20business%20management%20institutions%2C%20choosing%20to%20return%20to%20India%20to%20settle%20here%20after%20a%20few%20years%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20picture%20that%20emerges%20matches%20the%20slogan%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20presidentship%3A%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EVasudhaiva%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EKutumbakam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98the%20world%20is%20one%20family.%E2%80%99%3Cspan%3E%20For%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eexpatriate%20diaspora%20families%20moving%20between%20home%20and%20the%20world%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20world%20as%20one%20family%20has%20acquired%20a%20tangible%20form%20of%20lived%20experience%20beyond%20the%20origins%20in%20abstract%20notions%20of%20universal%20humanity%20and%20fraternity.%20A%20global%2C%20cosmopolitan%20culture%20is%20becoming%20pervasive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInevitably%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%20new%20opportunities%20and%20challenges%20present%20themselves%20to%20the%20sending%20and%20the%20receiving%20country.%20One%20delicate%20but%20distressing%20issue%20that%20has%20been%20arising%20repeatedly%2C%20has%20presented%20itself%20once%20again%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fbaby-ariha-shah-taken-from-parents-germany-8644093%2F%5C%22%3Eongoing%20saga%20of%20the%20Gujarati%20baby%20in%20Berlin%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20custody%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20child%20services%20agency%20of%20Germany%20after%20judicial%20orders%20were%20passed%20to%20deprive%20the%20parents%20of%20their%20parental%20rights.%20An%20appeal%20is%20pending%20even%20as%20the%20parents%20are%20deprived%20of%20simple%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20is%20the%20fate%20of%20Indian%20children%20removed%20from%20parental%20custody%20by%20foreign%20child%20services%20agencies%20and%20subjected%20to%20being%20brought%20up%20in%20an%20artificial%20environment.%20We%20were%20confronted%20with%20this%20issue%20during%20my%20tenure%20and%20that%20of%20my%20immediate%20predecessor%2C%20Mr%20S.M.%20Krishna%2C%20as%20external%20affairs%20minister.%20It%20also%20arose%20on%20the%20watch%20of%20my%20successor%20as%20Minister%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20the%20late%20Mrs%20Sushma%20Swaraj.%20In%20each%20case%20we%20put%20in%20our%20energies%20to%20find%20an%20immediate%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20children%20tend%20to%20be%20very%20young%3A%20infants%2C%20toddlers%20and%20primary%20schoolers.%20They%20are%20often%20unfamiliar%20with%20the%20local%20language%20and%20culture.%20The%20environment%20in%20the%20home%20they%20are%20taken%20from%2C%20including%20food%2C%20language%20and%20religious%20practice%2C%20is%20largely%20that%20of%20the%20home%20in%20India.%20Yet%20these%20children%20are%20placed%20in%20foster%20care%20of%20person%20who%20are%20native%20to%20the%20country%20of%20residence.%20The%20foster%20carers%20have%20no%20ethnic%20or%20cultural%20links%20with%20the%20child.This%20is%20an%20issue%20that%20does%20not%20confront%20India%20alone.%20Expatriate%20families%20from%20other%20countries%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20South%20America%2C%20Eastern%20Europe%20and%20Africa%20are%20similarly%20affected%20in%20the%20nations%20of%20Western%20Europe%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20North%20America%2C%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20such%20children%20are%20removed%2C%20home%20origin%20countries%20intervene%20on%3Cspan%3E%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3Ead%20hoc%3C%2Fi%3E%20basis%20to%20have%20them%20repatriated%20to%20their%20extended%20family%20or%20a%20foster%20placement%20in%20the%20home%20country.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20standard%20operating%20procedures%2C%20this%20involves%20protracted%20negotiations%20resulting%20in%20much%20distress%20all%20round%2C%20especially%20to%20the%20impressionable%20children%20involved.%20Sometimes%20parents%20are%20unable%20to%20withstand%20the%20pressure.%20A%20few%20days%20ago%20we%20had%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Faustralian-government-reviews-childrens-custody-after-death-of-indian-origin-mother%2Farticle67253033.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMs.%2520Patil%2527s%2520family%2520say%2520that%2Ctreated%2520for%2520a%2520severe%2520illness.%5C%22%3Etragic%20death%20by%20suicide%20of%20an%20Indian%20mother%3C%2Fa%3E%20whose%20children%20were%20confiscated%20by%20Australian%20child%20protection%20services.%20Amongst%20some%20prominent%20cases%20reported%20in%20recent%20years%20are%20the%20ones%20of%20Mrs%20Chatterjee%20(later%20featured%20in%20the%20film%20%3Cem%3EMrs%20Chatterjee%20vs%20Norway%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fmrs-shah-vs-germany-mother-fights-for-rights-of-2-5-year-old%2Farticleshow%2F102659177.cms%5C%22%3EMrs%20Shah%20v%20Germany%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Faustralian-government-reviews-childrens-custody-after-death-of-indian-origin-mother%2Farticle67253033.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMs.%2520Patil%2527s%2520family%2520say%2520that%2Ctreated%2520for%2520a%2520severe%2520illness.%5C%22%3EMrs%20Patil%20v%20Australia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mrs%20Yusuf%20v%20England%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Feast%2Fstory%2Fcustody-row-sweden-india-origin-child-norway-100919-2012-05-01%5C%22%3EMrs%20Annie%20Johansson%20v%20Sweden%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0To%20avoid%20further%20such%20tragedies%2C%20there%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20for%20the%20international%20community%20to%20develop%20a%20protocol%20for%20the%20repatriation%20of%20children%20removed%20from%20their%20parents%20by%20foreign%20child%20services.%20When%20the%20home%20country%20is%20willing%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20the%20safety%20and%20welfare%20of%20the%20child%2C%20as%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20done%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Gujarati%20baby%20in%20Germany%2C%20there%20would%20appear%20to%20be%20no%20reason%20to%20refuse%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20must%20respect%20foreign%20legal%20systems%20for%20intervening%20to%20remove%20children%20that%20they%20believe%20are%20at%20risk%20or%20victims%20child%20abuse%2C%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20without%20at%20present%20dealing%20with%20the%20parents%E2%80%99%20claims%20of%20cultural%20bias%20and%20lack%20of%20due%20process%2C%20the%20fate%20of%20such%20children%20must%20not%20be%20decided%20on%20a%20technical%20and%20jurisdictional%20basis.%20The%20essential%20humanity%20of%20the%20child%20must%20be%20paramount%20and%20the%20ethnocultural%20backdrop%20not%20be%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20reported%20that%20several%20top%20former%20judges%20of%20the%20high%20courts%20have%20written%20to%20the%20G20%20to%20seek%20a%20compassionate%20and%20reasonable%20solution%20to%20this%20human%20problem.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Indian%20government%20will%20hopefully%20initiate%20a%20dialogue%20on%20this%20issue%20at%20the%20G20%20Summit%20despite%20a%20full%20agenda%20and%20that%20we%20can%20hear%20the%20news%20that%20the%20Gujarati%20baby%20will%20return%20from%20Germany%20to%20India.%20And%20a%20humane%20protocol%20will%20be%20put%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESalman%20Khurshid%20is%20a%20former%20external%20affairs%20minister%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22