illie-eilish-peter-gabriel-gun-violence-1235714440%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Meta%20among%206%20tech%20giants%20deemed%20'gatekeepers'%20set%20to%20face%20strict%20competition%20rules%20under%20new%20EU%20law%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224977%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20illustration%20picture%20taken%20in%20London%20on%20December%2018%2C%202020%20shows%20the%20logos%20of%20Google%2C%20Apple%2C%20Facebook%2C%20Amazon%20and%20Microsoft%20displayed%20on%20a%20mobile%20phone%20with%20an%20EU%20flag%20displayed%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f8629ca35dd100195eed7f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223318%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%2C%20Apple%2C%20Facebook%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20logos%20displayed%20in%20front%20of%20an%20EU%20flag.%3Cp%3EJUSTIN%20TALLIS%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20European%20Union%20named%20six%20tech%20giants%20as%C2%A0%26quot%3Bgatekeepers%26quot%3B%20that%20have%20to%20comply%20with%20new%20laws.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Digital%20Markets%20Act%20aims%20to%20give%20more%20choice%20to%20users%20and%20open%20up%20the%20market%20for%20competitors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20TikTok%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%C2%A0%26quot%3Bfundamentally%20disagrees%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20designation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAlphabet%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Apple%2C%20TikTok%20parent%20ByteDance%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20have%20been%20designated%20as%20%26quot%3Bgatekeepers%26quot%3B%20set%20to%20face%20new%20rules%20in%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20lawmakers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fcommission%2Fpresscorner%2Fdetail%2Fen%2Fip_23_4328%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20tech%20giants%20have%20six%20months%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feu-rules-big-tech-dsa-dma-facebook-google-apple-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEU's%20Digital%20Markets%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20(DMA)%2C%20which%20aims%20at%20improving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolitical-power-tech-giants-limits-european-union-von-der-leyen-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompetition%20in%20the%20tech%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20today's%20designation%20we%20are%20finally%20reining%20in%20the%20economic%20power%20of%206%20gatekeepers%2C%20giving%20more%20choice%20to%20consumers%20and%20creating%20new%20opportunities%20for%20smaller%20innovative%20tech%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Thierry%20Breton%2C%20the%20commissioner%20for%20the%20EU's%20internal%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DMA's%20rules%20include%20a%20ban%20on%20preventing%20consumers%20to%20linking%20to%20businesses%20outside%20the%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20dispute%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepic-games-apple-war-fortnite-eu-antitrust-complaint-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20and%20%26quot%3BFortnite%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20saw%20the%20latter%20kicked%20off%20the%20App%20Store%20after%20encouraging%20users%20to%20pay%20on%20its%20own%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20act%20would%20also%20obligate%20platforms%20to%20let%20business%20users%20access%20data%20they%20generate%20in%20using%20the%20gatekeepers'%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20designations%20are%20split%20into%20various%20categories%20for%20the%20companies'%20services%2C%20such%20as%20social%20networks%2C%20search%2C%20and%20video%20sharing.%20Only%20Google%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Meta's%20ad%20businesses%20fall%20under%20the%20gatekeeper%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20identities%20of%20the%20gatekeepers%20aren't%20a%20surprise%2C%20but%20it%20is%20now%20about%20to%20get%20interesting%20in%20terms%20of%20who%20appeals%20the%20designations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Miranda%20Cole%2C%20antitrust%20and%20competition%20partner%20at%20Norton%20Rose%20Fulbright.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20shared%20with%20Insider%2C%20a%20TikTok%20spokesperson%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20support%20the%20DMA's%20goal%20of%20creating%20a%20competitive%20playing%20field%20in%20Europe%20but%20fundamentally%20disagree%20with%20this%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTikTok%20has%20brought%20choice%20to%20a%20space%20largely%20controlled%20by%20incumbents%20and%20this%20decision%20risks%20undermining%20the%20DMA's%20stated%20goal%20by%20protecting%20actual%20gatekeepers%20from%20newer%20competitors%20like%20TikTok%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20extremely%20disappointed%20that%20no%20market%20investigation%20was%20conducted%20prior%20to%20this%20decision%20and%20are%20evaluating%20our%20next%20steps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20announcement%2C%20Apple%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20remain%20very%20concerned%20about%20the%20privacy%20and%20data%20security%20risks%20the%20DMA%20poses%20for%20our%20users.%20Our%20focus%20will%20be%20on%20how%20we%20mitigate%20these%20impacts%20and%20continue%20to%20deliver%20the%20very%20best%20products%20and%20services%20to%20our%20European%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Meta%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20is%20evaluating%20the%20designations%20and%20will%20set%20out%20further%20information%20as%20it%20works%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20DMA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20delivering%20services%20that%20meet%20our%20customers'%20requirements%20within%20Europe's%20evolving%20regulatory%20landscape%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20will%20work%20%26quot%3Bconstructively%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Foutreach-initiatives%2Fpublic-policy%2Fbuilding-for-compliance-with-the-digital-markets-act%2F%5C%2