0about%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20to%20Russia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A107%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66727785%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66727785.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66727785.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ready%20To%20Work%20As%20Per...%3A%20Election%20Body%20Chief%20On%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20is%20ready%20to%20work%20as%20per%20constitutional%20provisions%20and%20the%20Representative%20of%20the%20People%20(RP)%20Act%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20said%20today%20in%20the%20context%20of%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20and%20other%20top%20ECI%20officials%20were%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20Bhopal%20to%20hold%20meetings%20with%20political%20parties%20and%20the%20administration%20and%20enforcement%20agencies%20over%20election%20preparedness%20in%20BJP-governed%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20polls%20are%20due%20by%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20voters'%20list%20will%20be%20published%20on%20October%205%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20state%20has%20nearly%205.5%20crore%20voters%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20concept%20of%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election%2C%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20(CEC)%20said%20that%20the%20poll%20commission%20is%20required%20to%20%26quot%3Bdeliver%20elections%20before%20the%20time%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20constitutional%20provisions%20and%20the%20RP%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20according%20to%20legal%20provisions%2C%20is%20five%20years%20from%20the%20date%20of%20the%20first%20sitting%20of%20Parliament%20after%20a%20new%20government%20is%20formed.%20The%20ECI%20can%20announce%20the%20general%20elections%20six%20months%20before%20the%20end%20of%20this%20time%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said.%20The%20norms%20are%20similar%20for%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20is%20mandated%20and%20ready%20to%20deliver%20elections%20as%20per%20legal%20provisions%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20last%20week%20formed%20a%20high-level%20committee%20under%20former%20president%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20to%20explore%20the%20feasibility%20of%20holding%20simultaneous%20polls%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20state%20assemblies%20and%20local%20bodies%2C%20bringing%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election%2C%20under%20the%20spotlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20about%20e-voting%2C%20CEC%20said%20it%20will%20take%20time%20as%20the%20process%20is%20vulnerable%20to%20hacking%20and%20also%20has%20trust%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20and%20the%20current%20process%20is%20not%20connected%20to%20a%20network%20but%20%26quot%3Bdiscussion%20on%20this%20(e-voting)%20is%20going%20on%20and%20it%20will%20take%20time%20to%20evolve%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20voters'%20list%20for%20MP%20polls%20will%20be%20published%20on%20October%205%2C%20said%20Mr%20Kumar%20and%20urged%20new%20eligible%20voters%20to%20get%20enrolled%20and%20apply%20for%20correction%20if%20they%20find%20any%20discrepancies%20in%20their%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20%26quot%3Bmisuse%20of%20online%20transactions%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20polls%2C%20the%20CEC%20said%20financial%20institutions%20are%20told%20to%20keep%20a%20watch%20on%20suspicious%20and%20bulk%20transactions%20and%20alert%20authorities%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20has%205.52%20crore%20voters%2C%20including%202.85%20crore%20male%20and%202.67%20female%20electors.%20The%20state%20also%20has%201%2C336%20transgender%20persons%2C%204.85%20lakh%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%207.12%20lakh%20voters%20aged%20above%2080%20years%2C%206%2C180%20people%20who%20are%20more%20than%20100%20years%20old%2C%2018.86%20lakh%20new%20voters%20and%2075%2C426%20service%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20said%20ECI%20is%20putting%20in%20place%20a%20system%20to%20enable%20senior%20citizens%20and%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20to%20vote%20from%20their%20homes%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls%20if%20they%20apply%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20voters%20can%20request%20through%20an%20online%20form%20to%20vote%20from%20home%2C%20he%20said.%20Election%20officials%20will%20visit%20the%20homes%20of%20such%20voters%20and%20ensure%20voting%20with%20confidentiality%20and%20also%20videograph%20the%20process%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20political%20parties'%20representatives%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20commission%20is%20also%20making%20efforts%20to%20increase%20voting%20percentage%20and%20ensure%20the%20participation%20of%20women%2C%20new%20voters%20and%20other%20vulnerable%20tribal%20groups%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20current%20expenses%20of%20candidates%20whose%20names%20have%20already%20been%20announced%20by%20their%20parties%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20as%20per%20legal%20provisions%2C%20a%20candidate%20is%20needed%20to%20keep%20a%20tab%20of%20their%20expenditure%20from%20the%20date%20of%20nomination%20till%20the%20polling%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20has%20already%20announced%2039%20candidates%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20has%20230%20assembly%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20freebies%2C%20the%20CEC%20said%20political%20parties%20have%20the%20right%20to%20inform%20voters%20about%20what%20they%20are%20offering%20to%20the%20electors%20but%20they%20also%20need%20to%20spell%20out%20the%20timeline%20of%20fulfilling%20the%20promise%2C%20the%20expenditure%20to%20be%20incurred%20on%20it%20and%20the%20arrangement%20of%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EECI%20has%20made%20a%20detailed%20report%20in%20this%20regard%20but%20the%20issue%20of%20freebies%20in%20polls%20is%20sub-judice%20with%20the%20matter%20reaching%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reply%20to%20another%20question%2C%20he%20said%20jail%20inmates%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20vote%20as%20per%20the%20law.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694000040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fimqcng1g_chief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar-pti_625x300_28_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fready-to-work-as-per-chief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar-on-one-nation-one-election-4364917%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20is%20ready%20to%20work%20as%20per%20constitutional%20provisions%20and%20the%20Representative%20of%20the%20People%20(RP)%20Act%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20said%20today%20in%20the%20context%20of%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fready-to-work-as-per-chief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar-on-one-nation-one-election-4364917%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fready-to-work-as-per-chief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar-on-one-nation-one-election-4364917%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fready-to-work-as-per-chief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar-on-one-nation-one-election-4364917%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20warns%20against%20'new%20Cold%20War'%20as%20big%20powers%20meet%20in%20South%20Asia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693999862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toii