%20not%20the%20ones%20following%20the%20great%20bubbles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E5.%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20very%20important.%20But%20it's%20perhaps%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-crisis-risk-heating-up-high-interest-rates-2023-9%5C%22%3Etoo%20little%2C%20too%20late%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20save%20us%20from%20a%20recession.%20The%20deflationary%20forces%20from%20the%20tech%20stocks%20breaking%20in%202021%20%E2%80%94%20probably%20too%20big.%20The%20power%20of%20interest%20rates%20rising%20and%20depressing%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dreal%2Bestate%2Bbusiness%2Binsider%2Btheron%26oq%3Dreal%2Bestate%2Bbusiness%2Binsider%2Btheron%26aqs%3Dchrome..69i57j33i160.4969j0j4%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal%20estate%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20very%20negative%2C%20slow-moving%20influence.%20I%20suspect%20that%20they%20will%20once%20again%20dominate%2C%20and%20we%20will%20have%20a%20recession%20running%20perhaps%20deep%20into%20next%20year%2C%20and%20an%20accompanying%20decline%20in%20stock%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E6.%20%26quot%3BThe%20economy%2C%20and%20particularly%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20are%20very%20secondary%20to%20a%20list%20of%20important%20long-term%20problems%20that%20we%20have%20that%20no%20one%20takes%20seriously%20enough%20yet.%20When%20we%20sit%20here%20discussing%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20we're%20a%20little%20like%20Emperor%20Nero%20fiddling%20while%20Rome%20burns.%26quot%3B%20(Grantham%20pointed%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20widespread%20inequality%2C%20and%20population%20declines%20in%20several%20countries%20as%20examples.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E7.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20market%20made%20a%20magnificent%20move%20from%20its%20all-time%20high%20in%20early%201998.%20It%20went%20straight%20up%20until%20March%20of%202000.%20Our%20clients%20did%20not%20approve%20of%20us%20being%2