tent%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06162148%2FThe_first_Indian_Governor_General_of_India_C._R._Rajagopalachari_had_a_Gandhian_air_and_was_very_popular_cropped.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EEconomic%20liberalization%20and%20the%20ascent%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%20have%20characterized%20Indian%20politics%20and%20economy%20since%20the%201990s.%20A%20wave%20of%20anti-incumbency%20took%20down%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20coalition%20government%20in%202014.%20The%20verdict%20brought%20the%20BJP%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20campaign%20targeting%20the%20corruption%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%20It%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20the%20Swatantra%20Party%20(1959-74)%2C%20long%20forgotten%2C%20has%20returned%20to%20public%20memory.%20Calls%20for%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20revival%20have%20been%20made%20by%20everyone%20from%20Amartya%20Sen%20to%20Ramachandra%20Guha.%20While%20the%20two%20have%20disagreed%20on%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20one%20may%20appropriate%20India%E2%80%99s%20past%2C%20both%20are%20committed%20to%20religious%20pluralism%20and%20have%20unambiguously%20condemned%20the%20BJP%20on%20grounds%20of%20majoritarian%20ideology%20and%20practice.%C2%A0%20In%20a%20public%20address%2C%20Sen%20expressed%20his%20wish%20that%20the%20Swatantra%20Party%20would%20be%20revived.%20Guha%20has%20asked%20whether%20India%20has%20any%20conservative%20intellectuals%20to%20speak%20of%20and%20has%20pointed%20to%20C.%20Rajagopalachari%20as%20a%20worthy%20model%20for%20a%20rejuvenated%20Indian%20conservatism.%20Though%20neither%20would%20join%20such%20a%20party%20or%20even%20vote%20for%20it%2C%20they%20believe%20that%20it%20could%20help%20protect%20democratic%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20291px)%2085vw%2C%20291px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06155210%2F0691205248.01.S001.JUMBOXXX.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22291%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06155210%2F0691205248.01.S001.JUMBOXXX.jpg%20789w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06155210%2F0691205248.01.S001.JUMBOXXX-197x300.jpg%20197w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06155210%2F0691205248.01.S001.JUMBOXXX-673x1024.jpg%20673w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671698%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22443%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAditya%20Balasubramanian%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EToward%20a%20Free%20Economy%3A%20Swatantra%20and%20Opposition%20Politics%20in%20Democratic%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EPrinceton%20University%20Press%2FPenguin%20India%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFree%20economy%20and%20the%20Swatantra%20Party%20came%20to%20life%20after%20India%20won%20freedom%20from%20the%20British%20Raj%2C%20once%20the%20consensus%20forged%20among%20anticolonial%20nationalists%20of%20diverse%20persuasions%20broke%20down.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%201950s%2C%20new%20economic%20interests%20had%20emerged%20and%20the%20Nehruvian%20model%20of%20planned%20developmentalism%20encountered%20roadblocks.%20As%20India%E2%80%99s%20literate%20public%20expanded%20in%20size%2C%20ideological%20entrepreneurs%20representing%20various%20causes%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%20urban%20spaces%20came%20together%20to%20critique%20Indian%20political%20economy%20and%20economic%20policy%20during%20the%20second%20plan%20period.%20They%20drew%20upon%20Cold%20War%E2%80%93era%20discourses%20of%20neoliberalism%20and%20tried%20to%20reconcile%20them%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%20and%20current%20conditions.%20Interacting%20in%20associations%20and%20writing%20in%20periodicals%2C%20they%20threshed%20out%20their%20own%20common-sense%20ideas%20to%20help%20make%20the%20economy%20the%20new%20domain%20for%20debate%20on%20the%20nation.%20Their%20free%20economy%20offered%20an%20ideological%20foundation%20for%20Indian%20conservative%20politics%20to%20develop%20in%20a%20distinctively%20mid-twentieth%20century%20form%20that%20blended%20an%20anticommunism%2C%20which%20invoked%20the%20fear%20of%20totalitarianism%2C%20with%20advocacy%20of%20unfettered%20commercial%20exchange%20and%20the%20defense%20of%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESituated%20in%20distinct%20contexts%20of%20region%2C%20language%2C%20caste%2C%20and%20political%20economy%2C%20the%20keyword%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20economy%E2%80%9D%20took%20on%20multiple%20meanings%20as%20it%20circulated%2C%20moving%20across%20metropole%20and%20mofussil%20alike.%20Most%20clearly%2C%20it%20meant%20opposition%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Csocialistic%20pattern%20of%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20Rajagopalachari%20dubbed%20permit-and-license%20raj.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20no%20other%20party%20explicitly%20disavowed%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20socioeconomic%20objectives.%20Free%20economy%20could%20also%20mean%20N.%20G.%20Ranga%E2%80%99s%20self-employed%20economy%20of%20peasants%2C%20Masani%E2%80%99s%20country%20of%20free%20enterprisers.%20It%20could%20be%2C%20to%20those%20Indians%20who%20took%20it%20upon%20themselves%20to%20write%20to%20the%20Swatantra%20leadership%2C%20a%20rhetoric%20for%20the%20expression%20of%20economic%20resentment.%20Of%20course%2C%20free%20for%20some%20meant%20unfree%20for%20others%3B%20the%20unspoken%20dimensions%20of%20the%20free%20economy%20discourses%20point%20to%20a%20patriarchal%20household%20division%20of%20labor%2C%20patterns%20of%20lower-caste%20exploitation%2C%20and%20not%20much%20freedom%20for%20the%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFree%20economy%E2%80%99s%20ambiguity%20allowed%20it%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20point%20of%20consensus%20agreed%C2%A0%20upon%20by%20diverse%20figures%2C%20whose%20social%20commitments%20ranged%20from%20cosmopolitan%20individualism%20to%20a%20parochial%20family%20orientation.%20The%20lowest%20common%C2%A0%20denominator%20of%20the%20varying%20visions%20of%20free%20economy%20were%20a%20decentralized%20economy%20with%20strong%20private%20property%20rights%2C%20which%20prioritized%20small%20industry%20and%20embraced%20agriculture.%20An%20antistatism%2C%20rather%20than%20an%20anarchism%2C%20pervaded%20these%20visions%3B%20the%20state%20would%20avoid%20its%20own%20commercial%20activity%20in%20such%20an%20economy%20and%20create%20a%20supportive%20environment%20for%20private%20economic%20activity%20when%20necessary.%20It%20would%20not%20occupy%20the%20commanding%20heights%20of%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20partisans%20of%20free%20economy%20interacted%20with%20libertarians%20and%20neoliberals%20in%20the%20Western%20world%2C%20finding%20occasional%20overlap%20in%20their%20concerns.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20content%20of%20their%20formulations%20shared%20more%20with%20those%20of%20American%20individualist%20anarchists%20than%20neoliberals.%20Indian%20protagonists%20engaged%20more%20with%20the%20polemical%20content%20of%20neoliberal%20utterances%20rather%20than%20theories%20of%20institutional%20design.%20They%20appropriated%20elements%20of%20these%20discourses%20for%20their%20political%20aims%2C%20as%20a%20layering%20over%20of%20their%20own%20economic%20ideas%20to%20respond%20to%20official%20Indian%20discourses%20on%20economy.%20This%20helped%20them%20wage%20a%20battle%20of%20ideas%20against%20the%20threat%20of%20communism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20381px)%2085vw%2C%20381px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06155537%2FScreenshot-2023-09-06-at-3.54.54-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22381%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06155537%2FScreenshot-2023-09-06-at-3.54.54-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06155537%2FScreenshot-2023-09-06-at-3.54.54-PM-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06155537%2FScreenshot-2023-09-06-at-3.54.54-PM-1024x1022.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06155537%2FScreenshot-2023-09-06-at-3.54.54-PM-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671704%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22380%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAditya%20Balasubramanian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFree%20economy%20became%20relevant%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20as%20a%20platform%20for%20a%20project%20that%20this%20book%20has%20described%20as%20opposition%20politics%2C%20embodied%20by%20the%20Swatantra%20Party.%20This%20was%20at%20one%20level%20an%20idea%20of%20an%20economically%20conservative%20party%20to%20balance%20out%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cone-footed%E2%80%9D%20democracy%2C%20imagined%20most%20coherently%20by%20Rajagopalachari%20but%20tracing%20antecedents%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Libertarian%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Rajagopalachari%E2%80%99s%20stature%20and%20appeals%20to%20dharma%20and%20ordered%20progress%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20attracting%20interest%20for%20this%20project%20across%20a%20range%20of%20political%20actors.%20Next%2C%20opposition%20politics%20rejected%20the%20anti-politics%20of%20development.%20It%20involved%20disseminating%20free%20economy%20in%20Indian-language%20publics%20and%20attaching%20it%20to%20a%20concrete%20political%20project.%20As%20they%20entered%20the%20world%20of%20party%20politics%20and%20elections%2C%20Swatantra%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20rewrote%20free%20economy%20for%20a%20middle-class%20rights-bearing%20citizen.%20To%20win%20popular%20support%2C%20the%20party%20tapped%20into%20a%20vein%20of%20discontent%20around%20issues%20such%20as%20inflation%20and%20taxation%20to%20establish%20itself%20as%20an%20alternative%20political%20player%20at%20the%20all-India%20level.%20It%20provided%20an%20economic%20education%20for%20voters%20from%20the%20lettered%20public%20and%20managed%20to%20mount%20what%20was%20at%20the%20time%20the%20largest%20organized%20political%20challenge%20to%20the%20Congress.%20As%20it%20did%20so%2C%20it%20drew%20on%20antecedent%20practices%2C%20most%20of%20them%20associated%20with%20the%20nationalist%20movement.%20These%20ranged%20from%20propaganda%20to%20mass%20protest.%20These%20efforts%20courted%20responses%20that%20showed%20how%2C%20in%20certain%20quarters%2C%20people%20understood%20opposition%20to%20the%20Congress%20as%20a%20forum%20for%20claim-making%20and%20expression.%20Finally%2C%20opposition%20politics%20meant%20using%20India%E2%80%99s%20institutional%20political%20machinery%20to%20forge%20coalitions%20and%20fight%20for%20free%20economy%20from%20elected%20office.%20Swatantra%20mobilized%20sections%20of%20the%20populace%20and%20used%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20institutions%20to%20provide%20checks%20and%20balances%20to%20the%20party%20in%20power%20before%20the%20elections%20of%201971%20swept%20it%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocracy%20is%20too%20often%20invoked%20to%20signify%20not%20merely%20a%20procedure%20of%20rule%20but%20also%20a%20set%20of%20values%E2%80%94freedom%2C%20rights%2C%20and%20progress%20among%20them.%20This%20conflation%20can%20mislead%20us%20and%20compromise%20our%20understanding%20of%20how%20distinct%20projects%20of%20democracy%20have%20emerged%20and%20unfolded.In%20India%2C%20the%20introduction%20of%20democracy%20before%20industrialization%20or%20the%20advent%20of%20mass%20literacy%20could%20mean%20that%20elections%20merely%20turned%20feudal%20relationships%20converted%20into%20legislative%20seats.%20No%20better%20example%20exists%20than%20the%20Maharani%20Gayatri%20Devi%E2%80%99s%20thumping%C2%A0%20victories%20under%20the%20Swatantra%20Party%20banner.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20democracy%20could%20carry%20the%20promise%20of%20emancipation%20for%20the%20masses%20and%20mean%20unprecedented%20empowerment%20for%20historically%20disadvantaged%20groups%20like%20Dalits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20world%2C%20the%20recent%20rise%20of%20ethnomajoritarian%20regimes%20has%20taken%20place%20in%20both%20democratic%20and%20undemocratic%20fashion.%20India%20is%20a%20peculiar%20case%20of%20the%20postcolonial%20society%20in%20which%20this%20process%20has%20taken%20place%20electorally.%20Consistently%20peaceful%20transfers%20of%20power%20have%20taken%20place%20between%20regimes%20for%20seven%20decades.%20But%20the%20Indian%20example%20also%20points%20to%20the%20risks%20that%20endure%20even%20after%20procedural%20democracy%20becomes%20ingrained%20in%20the%20postcolony.%20Projects%20like%20Swatantra%E2%80%99s%20can%20help%20us%20imagine%20alternative%20possibilities%20and%20solidarities%20to%20check%20the%20worst%20excesses%20of%20the%20present%2C%20even%20if%20they%20stand%20far%20apart%20from%20our%20utopias.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExcerpted%20with%20permission%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3EToward%20a%20Free%20Economy%3A%20Swatantra%20and%20Opposition%20Politics%20in%20Democratic%20India%3Cem%3E%20by%20Aditya%20Balasubramanian.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAditya%C2%A0Balasubramanian%20is%20a%20Senior%20Lecturer%20in%20History%C2%A0at%20the%20Australian%20National%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693999210000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06162148%2FThe_first_Indian_Governor_General_of_India_C._R._Rajagopalachari_had_a_Gandhian_air_and_was_very_popular_cropped.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fwhat-the-rise-of-the-swatantra-party-says-about-the-possibilities-of-indian-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Projects%20like%20Swatantra%20%5BParty%5D%E2%80%99s%20can%20help%20us%20imagine%20alternative%20possibilities%20and%20solidarities%20to%20check%20the%20worst%20excesses%20of%20the%20present%2C%20even%20if%20they%20stand%20far%20apart%20from%20our%20utopias.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fwhat-the-rise-of-the-swatantra-party-says-about-the-possibilities-of-indian-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBCCI%20Can't...%26quot%3B%3A%20After%20Lahore%20Visit%2C%20Binny%20Says%20This%20On%20IND-PAK%20Bilaterals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBCCI%20President%20Roger%20Binny%20could%20not%20stop%20gushing%20over%20the%20warm%20and%20friendly%20treatment%20they%20received%20in%20Pakistan%20on%20their%20short%20visit%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20nation%20while%20Board%20Vice%20President%20Rajeev%20Shukla%20asserted%20that%20cricket%20could%20be%20the%20bridge%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20that%20share%20a%20tense%20diplomatic%20relation.%20Binny%20and%20Shukla%20returned%20to%20India%20via%20the%20the%20Attari-Wagah%20border%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20watching%20Asia%20Cup%20matches%20on%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board's%20invitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20first%20instance%20in%2017%20years%20that%20the%20two%20BCCI%20office%20bearers%20travelled%20to%20Pakistan.%20They%20had%20crossed%20the%20border%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20very%20good%20meeting%20in%20Pakistan.%20We%20received%20very%20good%20hospitality.%20They%20took%20care%20of%20us%20very%20well.%20The%20main%20agenda%20was%20to%20watch%20cricket%20and%20to%20sit%20and%20discuss%20things%20with%20them.%20Overall%2C%20it%20was%20a%20very%20good%20trip%2C%26quot%3B%20Binny%20told%20PTI%20after%20their%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20treated%20us%20very%20well%2C%20they%20went%20out%20of%20the%20way%20to%20make%20us%20comfortable.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20countries%20compete%20against%20each%20other%20only%20in%20ICC%20or%20ACC%20events%20as%20bilateral%20cricket%20ties%20have%20been%20suspended%20due%20to%20diplomatic%20tension%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20an%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20travelled%20to%20Pakistan%20was%20back%20in%202008%20for%20the%20Asia%20Cup.%20Pakistan%20last%20hosted%20India%20for%20a%20bilateral%20series%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20last%20visited%20India%20in%202012%20for%20a%20white-ball%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20resumption%20of%20bilateral%20cricket%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20Binny%20reiterated%20that%20they%20can't%20take%20a%20call%20on%20that.%20%26quot%3BBCCI%20can't%20say.%20It%20is%20a%20government%20issue%2C%20and%20they%20will%20have%20to%20take%20a%20call.%20We%20need%20to%20wait%20and%20see.%20And%20hopefully%2C%20it%20will%20happen%20because%20the%20(ODI)%20World%20Cup%20is%20coming%20up%2C%20Pakistan%20team%20will%20be%20in%20India%20to%20play%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%20are%20currently%20engaged%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20will%20face%20off%20again%20in%20the%20much-anticipated%20World%20Cup%20clash%20on%20October%2014%20in%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there%20were%20reservations%20about%20Pakistan%20travelling%20to%20India%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20the%20PCB%20eventually%20agreed.%20Shukla%20also%20praised%20PCB%20for%20its%20hospitality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20meeting%20was%20very%20good.%20The%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20took%20very%20good%20care%20of%20us.%20The%20security%20was%20tremendous%2C%20all%20the%20arrangements%20were%20fabulous.%20It%20was%20a%20goodwill%20visit%20for%20cricket%20which%20went%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%20(ACC)%20President%20Mr%20Jay%20Shah%20is%20also%20BCCI%20secretary%2C%20so%20keeping%20in%20mind%20that%2C%20we%20had%20this%20visit.%20BCCI%20enjoys%20a%20good%20relationship%20will%20all%20the%20ACC%20members%2C%20that's%20why%20we%20also%20visited%20Sri%20Lanka.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20if%20cricket%20can%20be%20a%20medium%20to%20restore%20peace%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCricket%20has%20always%20been%20an%20important%20medium%20even%20before.%20Take%20the%202004%20tour%2C%20for%20example%3B%20the%20atmosphere%20that%20was%20created%20resulted%20in%20a%20great%20friendship%20and%20trade%20delegations.%20The%20shopkeepers%20were%20not%20even%20taking%20money%20from%20people%2C%20that%20was%20a%20great%20atmosphere.%26quot%3B%20The%20first%20game%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20in%20Asia%20Cup%20was%20washed%20out%20and%20the%20two%20teams%20will%20test%20each%20other%20again%20on%20Sunday%20in%20Colombo%20before%20a%20possible%20meeting%20in%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693999020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Flq4p8088_bcci-pcb-_625x300_04_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fbcci-cant-upon-arrival-from-lahore-board-president-roger-binny-says-this-on-resuming-india-vs-pakistan-bilateral-series-4364975%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BCCI%20President%20Roger%20Binny%20could%20not%20stop%20gushing%20over%20the%20warm%20and%20friendly%20treatment%20they%20received%20in%20Pakistan%20on%20their%20short%20visit%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20nation%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fbcci-cant-upon-arrival-from-lahore-board-president-roger-binny-says-this-on-resuming-india-vs-pakistan-bilateral-series-4364975%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fbcci-cant-upon-arrival-from-lahore-board-president-roger-binny-says-this-on-resuming-india-vs-pakistan-bilateral-series-4364975%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-c