me%20%26quot%3Buninvestible%26quot%3B%2C%20pointing%20to%20fines%2C%20raids%20and%20other%20actions%20that%20have%20made%20it%20risky%20to%20do%20business%20in%20the%20world's%20second-largest%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20restriction%20by%20China%20mirrors%20similar%20bans%20taken%20in%20the%20United%20States%20against%20Chinese%20smartphone%20maker%20Huawei%20Technologies%20(HWT.UL)%20and%20short%20video%20platform%20TikTok%2C%20owned%20by%20China's%20ByteDance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20one%20of%20Apple's%20biggest%20markets%20and%20generates%20nearly%20one-fifth%20of%20its%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693998480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ff8h80a58_iphone_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-bans-iphone-other-foreign-brands-for-government-officials-at-work-report-4364659%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20has%20ordered%20officials%20at%20central%20government%20agencies%20to%20not%20use%20Apple's%20iPhones%20and%20other%20foreign-branded%20devices%20for%20work%20or%20bring%20them%20into%20the%20office%2C%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20citing%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-bans-iphone-other-foreign-brands-for-government-officials-at-work-report-4364659%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-bans-iphone-other-foreign-brands-for-government-officials-at-work-report-4364659%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-bans-iphone-other-foreign-brands-for-government-officials-at-work-report-4364659%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netaji%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose's%20Grandnephew%20Resigns%20From%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChandra%20Bose%2C%20the%20grandnephew%20of%20Netaji%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%2C%20resigned%20from%20BJP%20today%20saying%20that%20the%20promises%20of%20propagating%20the%20nationalist%20leader's%20vision%20was%20not%20fulfilled%20by%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandra%20Bose%20had%20joined%20BJP%20in%202016%20and%20contested%20election%20twice%20on%20BJP%20ticket%20-%20in%20the%202016%20assembly%20and%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20joined%20BJP%20I%20was%20promised%20that%20I%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20propagate%20the%20inclusive%20ideology%20of%20Netaji%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%20and%20Sarat%20Chandra%20Bose.%20But%20nothing%20of%20that%20sort%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBose%2C%20who%20was%20appointed%20the%20West%20Bengal%20BJP%20vice-president%20in%202016%2C%20was%20dropped%20from%20it%20during%20the%202020%20organisational%20reshuffle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20discussions%20(with%20BJP)%20then%20centered%20on%20the%20inclusive%20ideology%20of%20the%20Bose%20Brothers%20(Netaji%20and%20his%20elder%20brother%20Sarat%20Chandra%20Bose%2C%20also%20a%20freedom%20fighter).%20My%20understanding%2C%20both%20then%20and%20later%2C%20had%20been%20that%20I%20would%20propagate%20this%20ideology%20across%20the%20country%20on%20the%20BJP%20Platform.%20It%20was%20also%20decided%20to%20form%20an%20Azad%20Hind%20Morcha%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20BJP%20with%20the%20primary%20objective%20to%20propagate%20Netaj's%20ideology%20of%20uniting%20all%20communities%20as%20Bharatiyas%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religion%2C%20caste%20and%20creed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20his%20resignation%20letter%20to%20BJP%20national%20president%20J%20P%20Nadda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20essential%20to%20keep%20the%20country%20united%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20ardent%20promotional%20efforts%20to%20achieve%20these%20laudable%20objectives%20have%20not%20received%20any%20support%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20either%20at%20the%20Centre%20or%20at%20the%20state%20level%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20I%20had%20put%20forward%20a%20detailed%20proposal%20suggesting%20a%20Bengal%20Strategy%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state.%20My%20proposals%20were%20ignored%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBose%20had%20time%20and%20again%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20state%20leadership%20over%20several%20issues%20and%20also%20opposed%20the%20CAA%20in%202019%2C%20going%20against%20the%20party%20line%2C%20Reacting%20to%20his%20resignation%2C%20BJP%20state%20spokesperson%20Samik%20Bhattacharya%20said%20%26quot%3BFor%20quite%20a%20long%20time%20he%20was%20not%20at%20all%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693998420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-01%2F0o74oes8_chandra-bose-ani-_625x300_20_January_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnetaji-subhas-chandra-boses-grandnephew-resigns-from-bjp-4364951%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chandra%20Bose%2C%20who%20was%20appointed%20the%20West%20Bengal%20BJP%20vice-president%20in%202016%2C%20was%20dropped%20during%20the%202020%20organisational%20reshuffle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnetaji-subhas-chandra-boses-grandnephew-resigns-from-bjp-4364951%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnetaji-subhas-chandra-boses-grandnephew-resigns-from-bjp-4364951%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnetaji