0to%20the%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20controversy%2C%20has%20said%20the%20remarks%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20minister%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20%26quot%3Bneeds%20proper%20response%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%20His%20response%20came%20a%20day%20after%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20cited%20the%20Central%20government's%20omission%20of%20an%20invite%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20for%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%20as%20an%20example%20of%20discrimination%20by%20practitioners%20of%20Sanatana%20dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%2C%20has%20refused%20to%20apologise%20for%20his%20comment%20that%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20akin%20to%20a%20disease%20and%20%26quot%3Bshould%20be%20eradicated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20he%20is%20ready%20to%20face%20any%20legal%20action%20for%20his%20comments.%20There%20are%20reports%20that%20attempts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20get%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Governor's%20sanction%20to%20initiate%20action%20against%20him.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20weekend%2C%20Udhyanidhi%20Stalin%20triggered%20a%20huge%20controversy%20with%20his%20remark%20that%20%26quot%3BSanatana%20(Dharma)%20is%20like%20malaria%20and%20dengue%20and%20so%20it%20must%20be%20eradicated%20and%20not%20opposed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20set%20off%20massive%20backlash%20on%20social%20media%20and%20prompted%20the%20BJP%20claim%20that%20it%20was%20equivalent%20to%20%26quot%3Ba%20call%20for%20genocide%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20the%20DMK%20leader%20has%20denied.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comment%20also%20put%20some%20allies%20of%20the%20new%20Opposition%20Bloc%20INDIA%20in%20a%20delicate%20spot%20ahead%20of%20a%20series%20of%20state%20elections%20by%20the%20year-end%20and%20the%20general%20election%20next%20year.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20taken%20a%20nuanced%20stance%2C%20saying%20all%20religions%20should%20be%20respected%20and%20p