d%20rising%20crude%20oil%20prices%20may%20further%20pressurise%20rupee.%20However%2C%20any%20intervention%20by%20the%20RBI%20and%20expectations%20of%20a%20no%20rate%20hike%20by%20Fed%20in%20its%20September%20FOMC%20may%20support%20rupee%20at%20lower%20levels.%20Traders%20may%20take%20cues%20from%20ISM%20services%20PMI%20data%20from%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%20On%20the%20domestic%20equity%20market%20front%2C%20the%2030-share%20BSE%20Sensex%20closed%20100.26%20points%20or%200.15%20per%20cent%20higher%20at%2065%2C880.52.%20The%20broader%20NSE%20Nifty%20advanced%2036.15%20points%20or%200.18%20per%20cent%20to%2019%2C611.05.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20Institutional%20Investors%20(FIIs)%20were%20net%20sellers%20in%20the%20capital%20markets%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20they%20offloaded%20shares%20worth%20Rs%201%2C725.11%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20exchange%20data.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693996800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-12%2Fnew-500-notes-cash-currency-pti_650x400_81482072336.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Frupee-falls-10-paise-to-close-at-all-time-low-of-83-14-against-us-dollar-4364754%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rupee%20depreciated%20by%2010%20paise%20and%20settled%20for%20the%20day%20at%20an%20all-time%20low%20of%2083.14%20(provisional)%20against%20the%20US%20dollar%20today%2C%20weighed%20down%20by%20a%20surge%20in%20crude%20oil%20prices%20and%20strong%20American%20currency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Frupee-falls-10-paise-to-close-at-all-time-low-of-83-14-against-us-dollar-4364754%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Frupee-falls-10-