20and%202%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20taken%20to%20an%20Assam%20Rifles%20camp%2025%20miles%20away%20has%20said%20that%20he%20sees%20Meiteis%20as%20his%20brothers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Seventy%20eight%20year%20old%20Reverend%20Prim%20Vaiphei%20says%20has%20%E2%80%9Calready%20forgiven%E2%80%9D%20the%20black%20sheep%20amongst%20them%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20terrible%20things%20done%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20am%20I%20to%20judge%20them%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20this%20morning%2C%20four%20days%20after%20he%20and%2023%20others%20like%20him%20belonging%20to%20five%20Kuki%20families%20were%20forcibly%20evicted%20from%20their%20homes%20shortly%20after%20midnight.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FzeU2Xy1BcYI%3Fsi%3DqL_iglG2RY9ubaYP%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2025-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Reverend%20Prim%20Vaiphei%20explains%20why%20he%20and%20his%20family%20along%20with%20four%20other%20Kuki%20families%20deliberately%20chose%20to%20remain%20in%20Imphal%20from%20May%203%2C%20when%20the%20trouble%20began%2C%20till%20September%201%2C%20when%20they%20were%20forced%20out%20by%20the%20state%20authorities.%20He%20says%20he%20trusted%20his%20life%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20his%20Meitei%20friends%20and%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20during%20the%20last%20four%20months%20houses%20around%20them%20were%20brunt%2C%20people%20killed%20and%20women%20raped%2C%20the%20Reverend%20said%20he%20trusted%20in%20god%20as%20well%20as%20the%20security%20provided%20by%20the%20state%20to%20keep%20him%20safe.%20He%20also%20relied%20on%20some%20of%20his%2