at%20were%20alleged%20to%20have%20been%20used%20by%20individuals%20connected%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group%20to%20purchase%20shares%20of%20the%20conglomerate%E2%80%99s%20listed%20companies%20have%20been%20closed%2C%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2F6-of-8-funds-used-to-invest-in-adani-shut-11693937876487.html%5C%22%3Ehas%20reported%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20regulatory%20filings%20in%20these%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20two%20Mauritius-based%20funds%20were%20shuttered%20last%20year%2C%20and%20a%20third%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20winding%20up.%20This%20follows%20the%20initiation%20of%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20markets%20regulator%20into%20offshore%20entities%E2%80%99%20holdings%20in%20Adani%20group%20companies%20in%202020%2C%20said%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20development%20presents%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20in%20identifying%20the%20ultimate%20beneficiaries%20of%20these%20investment%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Organized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%2C%20a%20global%20network%20of%20investigative%20journalists%2C%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.occrp.org%2Fen%2Finvestigations%2Fdocuments-provide-fresh-insight-into-allegations-of-stock-manipulation-that-rocked-indias-powerful-adani-group%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20two%20men%20who%20secretly%20invested%20in%20the%20Adani%20Group%20turn%20out%20to%20have%20close%20ties%20to%20its%20majority%20owners%2C%20the%20Adani%20family%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20violations%20of%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20rules%20on%20free%20float%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20men%20%E2%80%93%20Nasser%20Ali%20Shaban%20Ahli%20and%20Chang%20Chung-Ling%20%E2%80%93%20spent%20years%20trading%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%E2%80%99%20worth%20of%20Adani%20Group%20stock%2C%20said%20the%20OCCRP%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBoth%20have%20close%20ties%20to%20the%20Adani%20family%2C%20including%20appearing%20as%20directors%20and%20shareholders%20in%20affiliated%20companies%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20however%2C%20mentions%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20Chang%20and%20Ahli%E2%80%99s%20money%20for%20their%20Adani%20Group%20investments%20came%20from%20the%20Adani%20family.%20The%20source%20of%20the%20funds%20is%20unknown.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20documents%20obtained%20by%20OCCRP%20show%20that%20Vinod%20Adani%20used%20one%20of%20the%20same%20Mauritius%20funds%20to%20make%20his%20own%20investments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OCCRP%20shared%20its%20findings%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Faug%2F31%2Fmodi-linked-adani-family-secretly-invested-in-own-shares-documents-suggest-india%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F8d46b435-9725-46d4-80be-2cb3e276c4c9%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20has%20denied%20all%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20categorically%20reject%20these%20recycled%20allegations.%20These%20news%20reports%20appear%20to%20be%20yet%20another%20concerted%20bid%20by%20Soros-funded%20interests%20supported%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20foreign%20media%20to%20revive%20the%20meritless%20Hindenburg%20report.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20was%20anticipated%2C%20as%20was%20reported%20by%20the%20media%20last%20week%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adani.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fmedia-release%2Fadani-group-media-statement-on-occrp-report%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-india-needs-to-keep-track-costs%5C%22%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Acquisitions%3A%20Why%20India%20Needs%20to%20Keep%20Track%20of%20the%20Costs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20possible%20violation%20of%20free%20float%20norms%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20were%20based%20on%20the%20suspicion%20that%20certain%20prominent%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%E2%80%9D%20investors%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20were%20actually%20individuals%20closely%20associated%20with%20the%20group%20itself.%20If%20proven%20true%2C%20this%20would%20have%20violated%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20rules%20on%20minimum%20public%20shareholding%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20SEBI%20rules%2C%20a%20listed%20company%20has%20to%20ensure%20that%2025%25%20of%20its%20shares%20remain%20as%20free%20float.%20These%20shares%20are%20readily%20available%20for%20trading%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%20So%2C%20the%20promoters%20can%20hold%20only%2075%25%20of%20the%20shares.%20This%20means%20free%20float%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexcludes%20promoters%E2%80%99%20holding.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20violation%20of%20free%20float%20norms%20can%20lead%20to%20delisting%20of%20the%20company%20from%20the%20stock%20exchanges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20happened%20with%20Patanjali%20Foods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2015%2C%20stock%20exchanges%20froze%20the%20promoter%20shareholding%20of%20Patanjali%20Foods%20after%20the%20company%20failed%20to%20meet%20the%2025%25%20public%20shareholding%20within%20the%20stipulated%20time%20period.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fmarkets%2Fstock-exchanges-freeze-promoter-shareholding-of-patanjali-foods-123031501217_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20promoter%20stake%20in%20the%20Baba%20Ramdev-backed%20company%20is%20currently%20at%2080.82%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20had%20planned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bqprime.com%2Fbusiness%2Fpatanjali-foods-promoters-to-dilute-6-share-to-meet-minimum-shareholding-norms%5C%22%3Edilute%206%25%20stake%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20meet%20minimum%20public%20shareholding%20norms%20of%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-the-inorganic-strategy-behind-the-purchase-of-gangavaram-port%5C%22%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Acquisitions%3A%20The%20%E2%80%98Inorganic%20Strategy%E2%80%99%20Behind%20the%20Purchase%20of%20Gangavaram%20Port%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20shuttered%20offshore%20funds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20cited%20several%20names%20of%20some%20these%20closed%20funds%2C%20which%20would%20have%20helped%20the%20regulator%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20find%20the%20ultimate%20beneficiary%20and%20therefore%20helped%20in%20its%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsebi-adani-probe-extension-supreme-court%5C%22%3Ehas%20been%20investigating%3C%2Fa%3E%20whether%20the%20Adani%20Group%20violated%20any%20rules%20concerning%20minimum%20public%20shareholding%2C%20related%20party%20transactions%20and%20manipulation%20of%20stock%20prices%2C%20as%20alleged%20in%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fwhy-has-the-adani-hindenburg-issue-become-a-matter-of-national-concern%5C%22%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20US-based%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fexplainer-short-selling-futures-india-adani-stocks-hindenburg%5C%22%3Eshort%20seller%3C%2Fa%3E%20Hindenburg%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20business%20daily%2C%20the%20Bermuda-registered%20Global%20Opportunities%20Fund%2C%20registered%20on%20January%206%2C%202005%2C%20was%20shut%20on%20December%2012%2C%202006%2C%20according%20to%20regulatory%20filings%20in%20the%20island%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMauritius-based%20Assent%20Trade%20and%20Investment%20Pvt.%20Ltd%2C%20set%20up%20in%20April%202010%2C%20turned%20defunct%20in%20June%202019.%20Lingo%20Trading%20%26amp%3B%20Investment%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20incorporated%20in%20December%202009%2C%20closed%20in%20March%202015.%20Mid%20East%20Ocean%20Trade%20%26amp%3B%20Investment%20Pvt.%20Ltd%20was%20set%20up%20in%20September%202011%20and%20closed%20in%20August%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEM%20Resurgent%20Fund%20was%20set%20up%20in%20May%202010%20and%20shut%20down%20in%20February%20last%20year.%20Asia%20Vision%20Fund%2C%20set%20up%20in%20May%202010%2C%20appointed%20liquidators%20on%2020%20April%202020%20and%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20winding%20up%2C%20according%20to%20filings%20reviewed%20by%20%3Cem%3EMint.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20seventh%20fund%2C%20Emerging%20India%20Focus%20Funds%2C%20which%20was%20set%20up%20on%20May%2019%2C%202008%2C%20continues%20to%20be%20active.%20Details%20pertaining%20to%20Gulf%20Asia%20Trade%20and%20Investment%2C%20registered%20out%20of%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20could%20not%20be%20ascertained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffresh-adani-revelations-that-hint-at-regulator-sebi-inaction-could-hurt-indias-fatf-credibility%5C%22%3EFresh%20Adani%20Revelations%20That%20Hint%20at%20Regulator%20SEBI%20Inaction%20Could%20Hurt%20India%E2%80%99s%20Fatf%20Credibility%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20DRI%20letter%20to%20SEBI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20stands%20out%20in%20the%20OCCRP%20report%20is%20that%20SEBI%20had%20in%20January%202014%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%2C%20a%20federal%20anti-smuggling%20agency%2C%20on%20a%20case%20the%20latter%20was%20investigating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOCCRP%20reported%20that%20the%20DRI%20had%20evidence%20that%20money%20from%20the%20alleged%20over-invoicing%20scheme%20it%20was%20investigating%20had%20been%20sent%20to%20Mauritius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20indications%20that%20a%20part%20of%20the%20siphoned-off%20money%20may%20have%20found%20its%20way%20to%20stock%20markets%20in%20India%20as%20investment%20and%20disinvestment%20in%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Najib%20Shah%2C%20the%20DRI%E2%80%99s%20director%20general%20at%20the%20time%2C%20in%20the%20letter%20to%20then%20SEBI%20chief%20U.K.%20Sinha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20DRI%20case%2C%20money%20from%20the%20alleged%20scheme%20was%20sent%20to%20an%20Emirati%20company%20called%20Electrogen%20Infra%20FZE.%20This%20company%20then%20forwarded%20the%20resulting%20proceeds%20of%20about%20%241%20billion%20to%20a%20Mauritius-based%20holding%20company%20ultimately%20owned%20by%20Vinod%20Adani%20that%20had%20a%20similar%20name%2C%20Electrogen%20Infra%20Holding%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReporters%20were%20able%20to%20trace%20the%20onward%20flow%20of%20over%20%24100%20million%20of%20these%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mauritius%20company%20loaned%20the%20money%20to%20another%20Vinod%20Adani%20company%2C%20Assent%20Trade%20%26amp%3B%20Investment%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20%E2%80%9Cto%20invest%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20Asian%20equity%20market.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20beneficial%20owner%20of%20both%20Electrogen%20Infra%20Holding%20and%20Assent%2C%20Vinod%20Adani%20signed%20the%20loan%20document%20as%20both%20the%20lender%20and%20as%20the%20borrower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20money%20was%20placed%20into%20the%20GOF%2C%20the%20same%20intermediary%20used%20by%20Chang%20and%20Ahli%2C%20and%20then%20invested%20in%20both%20EIFF%20and%20Asia%20Vision%20Fund%2C%20another%20Mauritius-based%20investment%20vehicle%2C%20the%20OCCRP%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20Sinha%20acknowledged%20the%20letter%2C%20let%20alone%20acted%20on%20it%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1055231%2Fsebi-knew-about-allegations-against-adani-group-since-2014-letter-shows%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20not%20expect%20me%20in%20all%20fairness%20to%20remember%20everything%20what%20happened%20nine%20years%20ago%2C%20given%20that%20I%20retired%20from%20SEBI%20six%20years%20ago%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sinha%20told%20%3Cem%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20DRI%20letter.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20recollect%20what%20the%20facts%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%20this%20year%2C%20Sinha%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Fndtv-appoints-former-sebi-chairman-uk-sinha-as-non-executive-chairman-16279441.htm%5C%22%3Ewas%20appointed%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20non-executive%20chairman%20and%20additional%20director%20for%20NDTV%20till%20March%2026%2C%202025.%20Adani%20Group%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fcompanies%2Fadani-group-officially-becomes-majority-shareholder-in-ndtv%2Farticle66586670.ece%5C%22%3Emajority%20shareholder%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693994504000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F21181904%2Fadani-brothers.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2F6-out-of-8-offshore-funds-used-for-share-purchases-in-adani-firms-shut-down-amid-allegations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20development%20presents%20a%20challenge%20for%20SEBI%20in%20identifying%20the%20ultimate%20beneficiaries%20of%20these%20investment%20entities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2F6-out-of-8-offshore-funds-used-for-share-purchases-in-adani-firms-shut-down-amid-allegations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahead%20Of%20Ind-Pak%20Asia%20Cup%20Clash%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20Met%20Department%20Predicts...%22%