y-concerns-11693985466291.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbbott%20in%20India%20has%20voluntarily%20recalled%20Digene%20Gel%20antacid%20medicine%20manufactured%20at%20our%20Goa%20site%2C%20due%20to%20isolated%20customer%20complaints%20on%20taste%20and%20odour.%20There%20have%20been%20no%20reports%20of%20patient%20health%20concerns.%20Other%20forms%20of%20Digene%2C%20such%20as%20tablets%20and%20stick%20packs%20are%20not%20impacted%20and%20Digene%20Gel%20manufactured%20at%20our%20other%20production%20site%20is%20not%20affected%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20available%20in%20sufficient%20quantities%20to%20meet%20current%20demand%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20Abbott%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693992747000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06150126%2FDigene-mint-Gel-450ml.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fabbott-india-recalls-digene-gel-batches-after-dgci-advisory%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CPatients%20to%20discontinue%20Digene%20Gel%20which%20are%20manufactured%20at%20Goa%20facility%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DGCI%20said.%20The%20drug%20authority%20had%20also%20asked%20chemists%20and%20wholesalers%20to%20stop%20selling%20the%20product.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fabbott-india-recalls-digene-gel-batches-after-dgci-advisory%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Upon%20Pakistan%20Visit%2C%20BCCI%20Vice-President%20Reveals%20'Demand'%20Made%20By%20PCB%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20president%20Roger%20Binny%20and%20vice-president%20Rajeev%20Shukla%20arrived%20at%20Attari-Wagah%20border%20in%20Amritsar%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20concluding%20their%20visit%20to%20Pakistan.%C2%A0Binny%20and%20Shukla%20travelled%20to%20Pakistan%20following%20an%20invitation%20to%20members%20of%20the%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%20(ACC)%20and%20other%C2%A0cricket%C2%A0boards%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20to%20attend%20Asia%20Cup%20matches%20taking%20place%20in%20Lahore.%20They%20also%20met%20players%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20teams%20at%20a%20gala%20dinner%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShukla%20said%20that%20the%20visit%20was%20a%20good%20one%20and%20hospitality%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20was%20good.%20The%20board%20had%20demanded%20the%20resumption%20of%20cricketing%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20it%20would%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20centre%2C%20said%20Shukla.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20two-day%20visit%20and%20a%20good%20visit.%20The%20Governor%20hosted%20a%20dinner%20in%20our%20honour.%20The%20hospitality%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20was%20also%20good.%20Their%20demand%20was%20that%20cricket%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20should%20be%20resumed%2C%20we%20said%20it%20would%20be%20decided%20by%20govt%20and%20we%20would%20do%20whatever%20our%20govt%20would%20say.%20It%20was%20a%20cricket%20visit%20and%20there%20was%20no%20political%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shukla.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20Binny%20termed%20the%20visit%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfantastic%20experience%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20fantastic%20experience.%20Like%20when%20we%20played%20the%20test%20match%20in%201984%20the%20same%20hospitality%20was%20given%20to%20us.%20We%20were%20treated%20like%20kings%20over%20there%2C%20so%20it%20was%20an%20excellent%20time%20for%20us.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20meet%20all%20the%20Pakistan%20officials%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board.%20They%20are%20very%20happy%20with%20the%20outcome%20of%20us%20coming%20there%20as%20we%20were%20so%20happy%20to%20be%20there%20also%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Binny.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20final%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20in%20Pakistan%20will%20take%20place%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20Lahore%20between%20Bangladesh%20and%20Pakistan.%20It%20is%20the%20first%20match%20of%20the%20Super%20Four%20stage%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20which%20will%20be%20played%20in%20Colombo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Group%20A%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20India%20have%20qualified%20for%20this%20stage.%20From%20Group%20B%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Bangladesh%20have%20qualified.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20take%20on%20Pakistan%20on%20September%2010%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20on%20September%2012%20and%20Bangladesh%20on%20September%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693992720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fu2s77i2o_rajiv-shukla_625x300_04_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fupon-pakistan-visit-bcci-vice-president-reveals-demand-made-by-pcb-4364510%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shukla%20said%20that%20the%20visit%20was%20a%20good%20one%20and%20hospitality%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20was%20good.%20The%20board%20had%20demanded%20the%20resumption%20of%20cricketing%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20it%20would%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20centre%2C%20said%20Shukla.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fupon-pakistan-visit-bcci-vice-president-reveals-demand-made-by-pcb-4364510%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fupon-pakistan-visit-bcci-vice-pre