0advocate%2C%20in%20Prayagraj%20and%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Students%20Morcha%20(BSM)%2C%20an%20independent%20student%20forum%20in%20the%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%20in%20Varanasi.%20The%20NIA%20also%20conducted%20raids%20at%20the%20residences%20of%20advocate%20Soni%20Azad%2C%20also%20associated%20with%20the%20PUCL%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20social%20activist%20Ritesh%20Vidhyarthi%2C%20advocate%20Kripa%20Shankar%2C%20land%20rights%20activist%20Rajesh%20Chauhan%20and%20political%20activist%20Manish%20Azad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20conducted%20the%20raids%20in%20eight%20locations%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20Deoria%2C%20Varanasi%2C%20Chandauli%20and%20Azamgarh%20districts%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20FIR%20lodged%20in%20June%20against%20alleged%20Naxals.%20While%20the%20agency%20is%20yet%20to%20issue%20a%20public%20statement%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20raids%2C%20the%20PUCL%20and%20the%20BSM%20said%20the%20NIA%20officials%20seized%20mobile%20phones%2C%20SIM%20cards%2C%20laptops%2C%20books%2C%20pamphlets%2C%20magazines%20and%20other%20publications%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPUCL%20national%20president%20Kavita%20Srivastava%20accused%20the%20NIA%20of%20carrying%20out%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwitch%20hunt%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctyrannical%20act%E2%80%9D%20and%20demanded%20the%20immediate%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20FIR%20and%20a%20halt%20to%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EStop%20this%20witch%20hunt!%20Immediately%20withdraw%20the%20FIR%20and%20halt%20the%20investigation!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSeemaAzad%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SeemaAzad%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FNIA%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23NIA%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWitchHunt%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WitchHunt%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FRaids%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Raids%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FUttarPradesh%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23UttarPradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fy9DMQbv7Kw%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fy9DMQbv7Kw%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FLiTv9ctJdX%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FLiTv9ctJdX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20PUCL%20India%20(%40PUCLindia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPUCLindia%2Fstatus%2F1699309971773800473%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20lawyer%20K.K.%20Roy%2C%20who%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20PUCL%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20NIA%20has%20issued%20summons%20to%20the%20activists%20and%20students%20questioned%20in%20the%20raid%20to%20appear%20before%20its%20Lucknow%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBSM%20leaders%20raided%2C%20magazines%20seized%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkanksha%20Azad%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20BSM%2C%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20NIA%20to%20appear%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20September%C2%A0%2012%20for%20further%20inquiry.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20searching%20our%20office%2C%20they%20said%20they%20suspect%20us%20of%20being%20in%20touch%20with%20Maoists%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Akanksha%2C%20an%20MPhil%20scholar%2C%20who%20is%20originally%20from%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSM%20alleged%20the%20NIA%20sleuths%20had%20detained%20Akanksha%20and%20her%20colleague%20Siddhi%2C%20an%20MA%20Sociology%20student%2C%20during%20its%20raid%20of%20their%20office%20from%205.30%20am%20to%202%20pm%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20NIA%20team%20confiscated%20a%20mobile%20phone%2C%20two%20SIM%20cards%2C%20two%20laptops%2C%20and%20many%20magazines%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EMashal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EDastak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EAlternate%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%E2%80%98Go%20to%20Village%E2%80%99%20campaign%20reports%20of%20the%20BSM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20magazines%20are%20in%20public%20domain%20and%20work%20to%20make%20the%20people%20aware%20of%20the%20wrongdoings%20and%20society%20and%20work%20towards%20making%20a%20better%20and%20democratic%20society.%20It%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20government%20is%20afraid%20of%20these%20magazines%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BSM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20Azad%20is%20the%20author%20and%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EDastak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20described%20as%20a%20monthly%20non-commercial%20magazine.%20Akanksha%20told%20journalists%20in%20Varanasi%20that%20the%20raids%20were%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CModi%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20instilling%20fear%20in%20those%20who%20speak%20against%20it%2C%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20speak%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20anyone%20to%20speak%20against%20them%20or%20their%20oppression%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Targeted%20for%20earlier%20activism%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20raided%20by%20the%20NIA%20say%20they%20could%20have%20been%20targeted%20for%20their%20public%20activism%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20recent%20protests%20they%20participated%20in.%20The%20BSM%20has%20been%20active%20in%20raising%20issues%20related%20to%20sexual%20harassment%20on%20campus%20and%20reservation%20for%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20in%20hostels.%20On%20August%2027%2C%20the%20BSM%20was%20part%20of%20a%20protest%20%E2%80%98Pratirodh%20Sabha%E2%80%99%20(resistance%20meet)%20staged%20by%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%20students%20and%20concerned%20citizens%20outside%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20central%20varsity%20to%20raise%20voice%20against%20arrest%20of%20social%20and%20political%20activists%20in%20the%20name%20of%20terrorism%20and%20Naxalism%2C%20and%20the%20arrest%20of%20political%20activists%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Kaimur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSM%20has%20shed%20light%20on%20recent%20and%20alleged%20attempts%20at%20suppression%20of%20the%20Bihar-based%20Kaimur%20Mukti%20Morcha%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20which%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20Adivasi%20struggle%20in%20the%20Kaimur%20plateau%20against%20the%20%E2%80%9Cblatant%20land-grabbing%E2%80%9D%20of%20their%20lands%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20creating%20a%20tiger%20reserve%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20BSM%20was%20active%20in%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20searched%20Seema%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20house%20for%2012%20hours%20and%20seized%2043%20items%2C%20said%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeema%20Azad%20and%20Vishwa%20Vijai%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20Azad%2C%20who%20is%20the%20present%20president%20of%20the%20PUCL%E2%80%99s%20UP%20unit%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20Vishwa%20Vijai%20had%20been%20arrested%20in%20February%202010%20on%20charges%20of%20being%20members%20of%20the%20banned%20CPI%20(Maoist).%20They%20had%20been%20accused%20of%20being%20in%20possession%20of%20Maoist%20literature%20and%20charged%20with%20sedition.%20After%20more%20than%20two%20years%20in%20jail%2C%20in%20June%202012%2C%20they%20were%20convicted%20by%20a%20lower%20court%20and%20awarded%20life%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202012%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fallahabad-hc-grants-bail-to-seema-azad-vishvijay-who-were-convicted-for-waging-war-against-nation%2Farticleshow%2F15373812.cms%5C%22%3Ea%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20granted%20the%20couple%20bail%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20coming%20out%20of%20prison%2C%20she%20has%20led%20many%20PUCL%20fact-finding%20teams%20against%20the%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20She%20is%20also%20the%20editorial%20committee%20of%20the%20PUCL%20National%20Bulletin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PUCL%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20it%20%E2%80%9Cbelieves%20that%20this%20operation%20of%20the%20NIA%20is%20a%20serious%20attempt%20to%20stifle%20the%20voices%20of%20an%20active%20human%20rights%20and%20democracy%20defender.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20clear%20attempt%20to%20intimidate%20Indian%20citizens%20who%20want%20to%20raise%20democratic%20demands%20and%20seeking%20accountability%20from%20public%20officials%20and%20the%20political%20executive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKripa%20Shankar%2C%20Manish%20Azad%2C%20Anita%20Srivastava%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKripa%20Shankar%2C%20an%20advocate%20who%20was%20also%20questioned%20by%20the%20NIA%2C%20was%20a%20co-accused%20in%20the%202010%20case%2C%20said%20lawyer%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20also%20interrogated%20Manish%20Azad%2C%20Seema%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20for%20several%20hours.%20In%20July%202019%2C%20the%20UP%20Anti-Terrorist%20Squad%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsabrangindia.in%2Farticle%2Fats-arrest-activist-couple-bhopal-accuses-them-having-maoist-links%2F%5C%22%3Earrested%20Manish%20aka%20Manish%20Srivastava%20and%20his%20wife%20Anita%20Srivastava%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20their%20residence%20in%20Bhopal%20over%20alleged%20links%20to%20Naxal%20ideology.%20They%20were%20later%20granted%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManish%20and%20his%20wife%20both%20work%20as%20professional%20translators%20and%20are%20natives%20of%20Machhlishahr%20in%20Jaunpur%20district%20in%20East%C2%A0UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20ATS%20theory%20as%20concocted%2C%20Seema%20Azad%20had%20in%202019%20said%20that%20Manish%20and%20Anita%20were%20political%20and%20social%20activists%20with%20a%20record%20of%20translation%20and%20academic%20work.%20Anita%20had%20penned%20several%20poems%20and%20stories%20under%20the%20pen%20name%20Shireen.%20She%20translated%20%E2%80%98Let%20me%20Speak%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20testimony%20of%20Bolivian%20labour%20leader%20Domitila%20Barrios%2C%20into%20Hindi%2C%20and%20has%20a%20PhD%20in%20oral%20history.%20Manish%20completed%20his%20MA%20in%20Hindi%20from%20Gorakhpur%20University%20after%20graduating%20from%20Allahabad%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20when%20the%20ATS%20had%20apprehended%20them%2C%20the%20agency%20had%20accused%20them%20of%20living%20in%20Bhopal%20under%20false%20identities%20and%20using%20false%20documents%2C%20and%20booked%20them%20for%20forgery.%20The%20ATS%20had%20then%20also%20picked%20up%20six%20other%20activists%20in%20three%20locations%20in%20Deoria%20and%20Kanpur%20but%20released%20them%20after%20questioning%20and%20seizing%20their%20laptops%2C%20pen%20drives%2C%20mobile%20phone%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20data%20extraction.%20Kripa%20Shankar%2C%20who%20also%20runs%20an%20anti-fascist%20front%20and%20his%20wife%20Vrinda%2C%20a%20teacher%20in%20a%20private%20school%2C%20were%20among%20those%20interrogated%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoni%20Azad%20and%20others%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20advocate%20Soni%20Azad%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20PUCL%2C%20her%20husband%20Ritesh%20Vidyarthi%20is%20former%20BHU%20student%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Mehnatkash%20Mukti%20Morcha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residence%20of%20Rajesh%20Chauhan%2C%20a%20land%20rights%20activist%2C%20who%20is%20among%20those%20leading%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20protest%20against%20land%20acquisition%20for%20an%20airport%20in%20Khiriya%20Bagh%20in%20Azamgarh%2C%20was%20also%20searched%20in%20Deoria%20by%20the%20NIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%E2%80%99s%20raids%20in%20Eastern%20UP%20come%20three%20weeks%20after%20the%20UP%20ATS%20arrested%20five%20persons%2C%20including%20a%20woman%2C%20from%20Ballia%20on%20charges%20of%20allegedly%20spreading%20Maoist%20ideology%20in%20border%20districts%20of%20UP%20through%20proxy%20outfits%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20plotting%20an%20armed%20rebellion%20against%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20were%20identified%20as%20Tara%20Devi%2C%20Lallu%20Ram%2C%20Satya%20Prakash%20Verma%2C%20Ram%20Murat%20Rajbhar%20and%20Vinod%20Sahni%2C%20all%20of%20Ballia%20in%20East%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENIA%E2%80%99s%20reaction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20NIA%20said%20it%20had%20%E2%80%9Ccracked%20down%E2%80%9D%20against%20attempts%20by%20leaders%2C%20cadres%20etc.%20of%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20to%20revive%20the%20banned%20terrorist%20organisation%20with%20raids%20across%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20raids%20were%20conducted%20at%20the%20premises%20of%20%E2%80%9Caccused%20and%20suspects%E2%80%9D%20at%20eight%20locations%20in%20UP%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20digital%20devices%2C%20including%20mobile%20phones%2C%20laptops%2C%20pen%20drives%2C%20compact%20discs%20and%20memory%20cards%20were%20seized%20during%20the%20raids%2C%20along%20with%20SIM%20cards%2C%20Naxal%20literature%2C%20books%2C%20pamphlets%2C%20pocket%20diaries%2C%20money%20receipt%20books%20and%20other%20incriminating%20documents%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency%20added%20that%20its%20investigations%20indicate%20that%20several%20frontal%20organisations%20and%20students%20wings%20have%20been%20tasked%20to%20motivate%20and%20recruit%20cadres%20and%20propagate%20the%20ideology%20of%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20with%20the%20intent%20of%20waging%20a%20war%20against%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20conspiring%20to%20commit%20acts%20of%20terror%20and%20violence%20in%20furtherance%20of%20this%20agenda%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%20that%20investigations%20also%20revealed%20that%20Pramod%20Mishra%20was%20leading%20the%20cadres%20and%20sympathisers%2Fover%20ground%20workers%20(OGWS)%20of%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20in%20the%20efforts%20to%20revive%20the%20terror%20organisation.%20The%20raids%20conducted%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20the%20case%20were%20at%20the%20premises%20of%20such%20cadres%20and%20OGWs%2C%20etc.%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20last%20month%2C%20Bihar%20Police%20had%20arrested%20Rohit%20Vidyarthi%2C%20the%20brother%20of%20Ritesh%20Vidyarthi%2C%20whose%20wife%20is%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20relating%20to%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRohit%E2%80%99s%20interrogation%20had%20further%20led%20the%20State%20Police%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20Pramod%20Mishra%2C%20CC%20Member%20and%20In-Charge%20of%20the%20NRB%20(Northern%20Regional%20Bureau)%20of%20CPI%20(Maoist).%20Following%20these%20arrests%2C%20the%20state%20police%20had%20seized%20arms%2C%20ammunition%20and%20a%20gun%20factory%2C%20where%20a%20lathe%20had%20been%20installed%20for%20making%20parts%20of%20weapons%20and%20assembling%20countrymade%20weapons%20in%20Bihar%20and%20UP%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20NIA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20filed%20by%20the%20NIA%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case%20earlier%20had%20named%20accused%20Manish%20Azad%2C%20Ritesh%20Vidyarthi%2C%20along%20with%20their%20associates%20Vishwavijay%2C%20Seema%20Azad%20and%20Manish%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Kripa%20Shankar%2C%20Soni%20Azad%2C%20Akanksha%20Azad%20and%20Rajesh%20Azad%20as%20some%20of%20the%20key%20accused%20working%20to%20further%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist)%E2%80%99s%20revival%20attempts%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693992471000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnia-raids-pucl-seema-azad-bsm-maoist%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Among%20others%2C%20NIA%20officials%20raided%20the%20house%20of%20rights%20activist%20Seema%20Azad%20in%20Prayagraj%20and%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Students%20Morcha%20(BSM)%2C%20an%20independent%20student%20forum%20in%20the%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%20in%20Varanasi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Tyrannical%20Act%2C'%20Say%20Activists%20as%20NIA%20Raids%20Rights%20Defenders%2C%20Students%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%C2%A0The%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20on%20August%205%20conducted%20simultaneous%20searches%20at%20the%20residences%20and%20offices%20of%20several%20activists%2C%20including%20the%20national%20secretary%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Union%20for%20Civil%20Liberties%20Seema%20Azad%2C%20and%20students%20in%20various%20cities%20of%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20purportedly%20to%20look%20for%20their%20alleged%20connection%20with%20the%20banned%20Naxalite%20organisation%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Maoist).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENIA%20officials%20raided%20the%20house%20of%20human%20rights%20activist%20Seema%20Azad%20and%20her%20husband%20Vishwa%20Vijai%2C%20an%20advocate%2C%20in%20Prayagraj%20and%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Students%20Morcha%20(BSM)%2C%20an%20independent%20student%20forum%20in%20the%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%20in%20Varanasi.%20The%20NIA%20also%20conducted%20raids%20at%20the%20residences%20of%20advocate%20Soni%20Azad%2C%20also%20associated%20with%20the%20PUCL%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20social%20activist%20Ritesh%20Vidhyarthi%2C%20advocate%20Kripa%20Shankar%2C%20land%20rights%20activist%20Rajesh%20Chauhan%20and%20political%20activist%20Manish%20Azad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20conducted%20the%20raids%20in%20eight%20locations%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20Deoria%2C%20Varanasi%2C%20Chandauli%20and%20Azamgarh%20districts%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20FIR%20lodged%20in%20June%20against%20alleged%20Naxals.%20While%20the%20agency%20is%20yet%20to%20issue%20a%20public%20statement%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20raids%2C%20the%20PUCL%20and%20the%20BSM%20said%20the%20NIA%20officials%20seized%20mobile%20phones%2C%20SIM%20cards%2C%20laptops%2C%20books%2C%20pamphlets%2C%20magazines%20and%20other%20publications%20from%20them.%20PUCL%20national%20president%20Kavita%20Srivastava%20accused%20the%20NIA%20of%20carrying%20out%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwitch%20hunt%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctyrannical%20act%E2%80%9D%20and%20demanded%20the%20immediate%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20FIR%20and%20a%20halt%20to%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20lawyer%20K.K.%20Roy%2C%20who%20is%20associated%20with%20the%20PUCL%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20NIA%20has%20issued%20summons%20to%20the%20activists%20and%20students%20questioned%20in%20the%20raid%20to%20appear%20before%20its%20Lucknow%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkanksha%20Azad%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20BSM%2C%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20NIA%20to%20appear%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20September%C2%A0%2012%20for%20further%20inquiry.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20searching%20our%20office%2C%20they%20said%20they%20suspect%20us%20of%20being%20in%20touch%20with%20Maoists%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Akanksha%2C%20an%20MPhil%20scholar%2C%20who%20is%20originally%20from%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSM%20alleged%20the%20NIA%20sleuths%20had%20detained%20Akanksha%20and%20her%20colleague%20Siddhi%2C%20an%20MA%20Sociology%20student%2C%20during%20its%20raid%20of%20their%20office%20from%205.30%20am%20to%202%20pm%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20NIA%20team%20confiscated%20a%20mobile%20phone%2C%20two%20SIM%20cards%2C%20two%20laptops%2C%20and%20many%20magazines%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EMashal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EDastak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EAlternate%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%E2%80%98Go%20to%20Village%E2%80%99%20campaign%20reports%20of%20the%20BSM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20magazines%20are%20in%20public%20domain%20and%20work%20to%20make%20the%20people%20aware%20of%20the%20wrongdoings%20and%20society%20and%20work%20towards%20making%20a%20better%20and%20democratic%20society.%20It%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20government%20is%20afraid%20of%20these%20magazines%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BSM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20Azad%20is%20the%20author%20and%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EDastak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20described%20as%20a%20monthly%20non-commercial%20magazine.%20Akanksha%20told%20journalists%20in%20Varanasi%20that%20the%20raids%20were%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CModi%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20instilling%20fear%20in%20those%20who%20speak%20against%20it%2C%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20speak%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20anyone%20to%20speak%20against%20them%20or%20their%20oppression%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20raided%20by%20the%20NIA%20say%20they%20could%20have%20been%20targeted%20for%20their%20public%20activism%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20recent%20protests%20they%20participated%20in.%20The%20BSM%20has%20been%20active%20in%20raising%20issues%20related%20to%20sexual%20harassment%20on%20campus%20and%20reservation%20for%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20in%20hostels.%20On%20August%2027%2C%20the%20BSM%20was%20part%20of%20a%20protest%20%E2%80%98Pratirodh%20Sabha%E2%80%99%20(resistance%20meet)%20staged%20by%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%20students%20and%20concerned%20citizens%20outside%20the%20gate%20of%20the%20central%20varsity%20to%20raise%20voice%20against%20arrest%20of%20social%20and%20political%20activists%20in%20the%20name%20of%20terrorism%20and%20Naxalism%2C%20and%20the%20arrest%20of%20political%20activists%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Kaimur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSM%20has%20shed%20light%20on%20recent%20and%20alleged%20attempts%20at%20suppression%20of%20the%20Bihar-based%20Kaimur%20Mukti%20Morcha%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20which%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20Adivasi%20struggle%20in%20the%20Kaimur%20plateau%20against%20the%20%E2%80%9Cblatant%20land-grabbing%E2%80%9D%20of%20their%20lands%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20creating%20a%20tiger%20reserve%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20BSM%20was%20active%20in%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20searched%20Seema%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20house%20for%2012%20hours%20and%20seized%2043%20items%2C%20said%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20Azad%2C%20who%20is%20the%20present%20president%20of%20the%20PUCL%E2%80%99s%20UP%20unit%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20Vishwa%20Vijai%20had%20been%20arrested%20in%20February%202010%20on%20charges%20of%20being%20members%20of%20the%20banned%20CPI%20(Maoist).%20They%20had%20been%20accused%20of%20being%20in%20possession%20of%20Maoist%20literature%20and%20charged%20with%20sedition.%20After%20more%20than%20two%20years%20in%20jail%2C%20in%20June%202012%2C%20they%20were%20convicted%20by%20a%20lower%20court%20and%20awarded%20life%20term.%20In%20August%202012%2C%20however%2C%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20granted%20the%20couple%20bail.%20Since%20coming%20out%20of%20prison%2C%20she%20has%20led%20many%20PUCL%20fact-finding%20teams%20against%20the%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20She%20is%20also%20the%20editorial%20committee%20of%20the%20PUCL%20National%20Bulletin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PUCL%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20it%20%E2%80%9Cbelieves%20that%20this%20operation%20of%20the%20NIA%20is%20a%20serious%20attempt%20to%20stifle%20the%20voices%20of%20an%20active%20human%20rights%20and%20democracy%20defender.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20clear%20attempt%20to%20intimidate%20Indian%20citizens%20who%20want%20to%20raise%20democratic%20demands%20and%20seeking%20accountability%20from%20public%20officials%20and%20the%20political%20executive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKripa%20Shankar%2C%20an%20advocate%20who%20was%20also%20questioned%20by%20the%20NIA%2C%20was%20a%20co-accused%20in%20the%202010%20case%2C%20said%20lawyer%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20also%20interrogated%20Manish%20Azad%2C%20Seema%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20for%20several%20hours.%20In%20July%202019%2C%20the%20UP%20Anti-Terrorist%20Squad%20had%20arrested%20Manish%20aka%20Manish%20Srivastava%20and%20his%20wife%20Anita%20Srivastava%20from%20their%20residence%20in%20Bhopal%20over%20alleged%20links%20to%20Naxal%20ideology.%20They%20were%20later%20granted%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManish%20and%20his%20wife%20both%20work%20as%20professional%20translators%20and%20are%20natives%20of%20Machhlishahr%20in%20Jaunpur%20district%20in%20East%C2%A0UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20ATS%20theory%20as%20concocted%2C%20Seema%20Azad%20had%20in%202019%20said%20that%20Manish%20and%20Anita%20were%20political%20and%20social%20activists%20with%20a%20record%20of%20translation%20and%20academic%20work.%20Anita%20had%20penned%20several%20poems%20and%20stories%20under%20the%20pen%20name%20Shireen.%20She%20translated%20%E2%80%98Let%20me%20Speak%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20testimony%20of%20Bolivian%20labour%20leader%20Domitila%20Barrios%2C%20into%20Hindi%2C%20and%20has%20a%20PhD%20in%20oral%20history.%20Manish%20completed%20his%20MA%20in%20Hindi%20from%20Gorakhpur%20University%20after%20graduating%20from%20Allahabad%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20when%20the%20ATS%20had%20apprehended%20them%2C%20the%20agency%20had%20accused%20them%20of%20living%20in%20Bhopal%20under%20false%20identities%20and%20using%20false%20documents%2C%20and%20booked%20them%20for%20forgery.%20The%20ATS%20had%20then%20also%20picked%20up%20six%20other%20activists%20in%20three%20locations%20in%20Deoria%20and%20Kanpur%20but%20released%20them%20after%20questioning%20and%20seizing%20their%20laptops%2C%20pen%20drives%2C%20mobile%20phone%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20data%20extraction.%20Kripa%20Shankar%2C%20who%20also%20runs%20an%20anti-fascist%20front%20and%20his%20wife%20Vrinda%2C%20a%20teacher%20in%20a%20private%20school%2C%20were%20among%20those%20interrogated%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20advocate%20Soni%20Azad%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20PUCL%2C%20her%20husband%20Ritesh%20Vidyarthi%20is%20former%20BHU%20student%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Mehnatkash%20Mukti%20Morcha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residence%20of%20Rajesh%20Chauhan%2C%20a%20land%20rights%20activist%2C%20who%20is%20among%20those%20leading%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20protest%20against%20land%20acquisition%20for%20an%20airport%20in%20Khiriya%20Bagh%20in%20Azamgarh%2C%20was%20also%20searched%20in%20Deoria%20by%20the%20NIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%E2%80%99s%20raids%20in%20Eastern%20UP%20come%20three%20weeks%20after%20the%20UP%20ATS%20arrested%20five%20persons%2C%20including%20a%20woman%2C%20from%20Ballia%20on%20charges%20of%20allegedly%20spreading%20Maoist%20ideology%20in%20border%20districts%20of%20UP%20through%20proxy%20outfits%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20plotting%20an%20armed%20rebellion%20against%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20were%20identified%20as%20Tara%20Devi%2C%20Lallu%20Ram%2C%20Satya%20Prakash%20Verma%2C%20Ram%20Murat%20Rajbhar%20and%20Vinod%20Sahni%2C%20all%20of%20Ballia%20in%20East%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693992471000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnia-raids-pucl-seema-azad-bsm-maoist%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Among%20others%2C%20NIA%20officials%20raided%20the%20house%20of%20rights%20activist%20Seema%20Azad%20in%20Prayagraj%20and%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Students%20Morcha%20(BSM)%2C%20an%20independent%20student%20forum%20in%20the%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%20in%20Varanasi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnia-raids-pucl-seema-azad-bsm-maoist%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata%20seeks%20control%20of%20Haldiram's%2C%20but%20snack%20maker%20wants%20...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693992258000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103432327%2Cimgsize-110422.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fta