20over%2C%20Afghanistan%20was%20289%2F8%20and%20still%20in%20the%20game.%20But%20Mujeeb%20ur%20Rahman%20was%20caught%20at%20long-on%2C%20following%20which%20the%20non-striker%20Rashid%20Khan%20sank%20to%20his%20knees%2C%20heartbroken%20to%20know%20that%20his%20team%20has%20been%20eliminated%20from%20the%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20he%20didn't%20know%20that%20the%20actual%20case%20was%20different.%20Afghanistan%20could%20have%20finished%20above%20Sri%20Lanka's%20Net%20Run%20Rate%20had%20they%20reached%20293%20after%2037.2%20overs%2C%20294%20after%2037.3%2C%20295%20after%2037.5%20overs%2C%20296%20after%2038%20overs%2C%20or%20297%20after%2038.1%20overs.%20Simply%20a%20big%20hit%20by%20the%20next%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Fazalhaq%20Farooqi%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112535-fazal-haque-playerprofile%5C%22%3EFazalhaq%20Farooqi%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20giving%20the%20strike%20to%20Rashid%20could%20have%20helped%20them%20finish%20the%20game%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20instead%2C%20Fazalhaq%20blocked%20the%20next%20two%20balls%2C%20before%20he%20was%20trapped%20leg-before-wicket%20while%20trying%20to%20defend.%20Afghanistan%20folded%20for%20289%20in%2037.4%20overs%20and%20lost%20by%20two%20runs.%20Lack%20of%20awareness%20about%20the%20net-run-rate%20equation%20resulted%20in%20Afghanistan's%20loss%20despite%20Rashid%2C%20a%20ferocious%20ball-striker%2C%20being%20there%20at%20the%20other%20end.%20Afghanistan%20walk%20out%20of%20the%20tournament%20without%20any%20win%20in%20their%20two%20group-stage%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fa6byZS456x%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fa6byZS456x%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Nihari%20Korma%20(%40NihariVsKorma)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNihariVsKorma%2Fstatus%2F1699225956710244369%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%