k%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-66714549.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-66714549.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hype%20Alone%20Cannot%20Sustain%20the%20G20%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20Presidency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06132900%2FF4b-BzwWoAADwXC.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20two%20stories%20running%20parallel%20to%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20G20%20summit%20being%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20later%20this%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eweek.%20One%2C%20that%20of%20the%20big%20Joes%20of%20the%20world%20meeting%20together%20for%20photo%20ops%20and%20backroom%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Enegotiations%20jostling%20for%20retaining%20or%20extracting%20deals%20based%20on%20their%20own%20interests%20and%20second%2C%20the%20host%20India%20running%20its%20own%20version%20of%20a%20public%20festival%20even%20as%20Delhi%20is%20being%20converted%20into%20a%20virtual%20fortress.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20problem%20with%20public%20festivals%20is%20that%20they%20have%20to%20have%20an%20expiry%20date%20and%20one%20begins%20to%20get%20tired%20if%20it%20is%20not%20backed%20by%20an%20encompassing%20sense%20of%20prosperity%2C%20security%20and%20peace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20before%20we%20come%20to%20India%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20look%20at%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20world%20right%20now.%20There%20are%20currently%20over%20700%20live%20conflicts%20happening%20around%20the%20world%2C%20some%20of%20which%20initiated%20by%20those%20very%C2%A0%20leaders%20coming%20together%20as%20this%20block.%20These%20hotspots%20include%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20South%20Sudan%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20Yemen%2C%20just%20to%20name%20a%20few%20alongside%20the%20new%20cold%20war%20between%20the%20Chinese%20and%20the%20America%20led%20block.%C2%A0%20Post-pandemic%20debt%20crisis%20has%20worsened%20specially%20for%20low%20income%20countries%2C%20multiple%20riots%20have%20become%20everyday%20phenomenon%20within%20countries%2C%20the%20rising%20economic%20inequalities%20continue%20to%20make%20rapid%20stride%20with%20the%20alarming%20rise%20in%20inflation%2C%20critical%20shortages%20of%20essential%20resources%20such%20as%20food%20and%20energy%20are%20a%20norm%2C%20anti-migration%20hysteria%20continues%20unabated%2C%20and%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis%20compounded%20by%20climate-related%20disasters%20as%20an%20everyday%20phenomenon%20is%20adding%20to%20the%20enduring%20aftermath%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20this%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20concerning%20erosion%20of%20democracy%20and%20human%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fg20-cities-forced-evictions-beautification%5C%22%3ENo%20Mercy%20for%20the%20Vulnerable%20as%20Authorities%20Beautified%20Urban%20Areas%20for%20G20%20Events%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20G20%20leaders%20need%20to%20demonstrate%20their%20dedication%20to%20democracy%20by%20signing%20and%20ratifying%20international%20human%20rights%20treaties%2C%20including%20the%20International%20Covenant%20on%20Civil%20and%20Political%20Rights%20(ICCPR)%2C%20and%20implementing%C2%A0%20the%20concluding%20observations%20made%20by%20the%20Committee%20for%20Civil%20and%20Political%20Rights%20(CCPR).%20By%20committing%20to%20and%20upholding%20these%20human%20rights%20treaties%2C%20the%20G20%20leaders%20can%20strengthen%20the%20protection%20of%20civil%20and%20political%20rights%2C%20which%20are%20essential%20for%20maintaining%20an%20inclusive%20and%20democratic%20global%20governance%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGlobal%20income%20poverty%20and%20hunger%20have%20increased%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20with%20700%20million%20people%20worldwide%20facing%20acute%20income%20poverty.%20Generally%20those%20trapped%20in%20poverty%20are%20from%20socially%20and%20politically%20excluded%20groups.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20this%20also%20stands%20in%20a%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20theme%2C%20%E2%80%98One%20Earth%2C%20One%20Family%2C%20One%20Future%E2%80%99%20put%20forth%20by%20the%20host%20Indian%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20can%20argue%20that%20surely%2C%20all%20this%20cannot%20be%20resolved%20by%20just%20a%20bunch%20of%20these%2020%20countries%20(which%20includes%20European%20Union)%2C%20which%20is%20more%20concerned%20with%20a%20limited%20set%20of%20priorities%20around%20global%20finance%2C%20debt%2C%20taxation%2C%20etc.%20However%2C%20one%20also%20knows%20that%20this%20collective%20group%20of%2020%20economies%20(consisting%20of%20diverse%20democratic%2C%20semi-authoritarian%20and%20authoritarian%20regimes)%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccounts%20for%20around%2080%25%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Egross%20world%20product%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0(GWP)%2C%2075%25%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Einternational%20trade%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%C2%A0two-thirds%20of%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eglobal%20population%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%2060%25%20of%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eworld%E2%80%99s%20land%20area%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESurely%2C%20this%20gives%20them%20enough%20heft%20to%20influence%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20happening%20around%20the%20world%20if%20they%20willed.%20Unfortunately%2C%20we%20have%20only%20seen%20them%20either%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20each%20other%20or%20simply%20engaging%20in%20pious%20and%20hollow%20statements.%20Also%2C%20they%20have%20shown%20no%20qualms%20about%20bypassing%20any%20multi-lateral%20mechanism%20proposed%20by%20UN%20when%20they%20wanted%20to.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20estimated%20that%20children%20lost%20about%2035%25%20of%20a%20normal%20school%20year%E2%80%99s%20worth%20of%20learning%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProlonged%20school%20closures%20have%20exacerbated%20existing%20educational%20inequalities%2C%20triggered%20anxiety%20and%20depression%20among%20students%20and%20contributed%20to%20child%20hunger%20by%20disrupting%20school%20meals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fposhan-tracker-anganwadi-icds-bengal-centre%5C%22%3EAs%20Bengal%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Political%20Tussle%20With%20the%20Union%20Plays%20Out%2C%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Nutrition%20Has%20Suffered%20Most%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20July%20has%20just%20been%20declared%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fjuly-2023-the-hottest-ever-month-on-record-likely-warmest-in-tens-of-thousands-of-years%5C%22%3Ehottest%20ever%20in%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20bringing%20unprecedented%20rains%20and%20floods%20in%20other%20regions%20of%20the%20world.%20As%20per%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%2C%20instead%20of%20reducing%20their%20emissions%20by%2045%25%20by%202030%2C%20based%20on%20the%20projections%20on%20the%20current%20efforts%20G20%20countries%20are%20only%20likely%20to%20reduce%20their%20emissions%20by%2010%25%20by%202030.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECollectively%2C%20the%20G20%20is%20responsible%20for%20around%2075%25%20of%20global%20greenhouse%20gases%20(GHGs)%20including%20land%20use%20change%20and%20forestry.%20We%20know%20that%20the%20G20%20leaders%20have%20the%20power%20to%20make%20substantive%20and%20equitable%20commitments%20within%20the%20revised%20National%20Determined%20Contribution%20(NDC)%20framework%2C%20setting%20forth%20ambitious%20goals%20for%20mitigating%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEqually%20crucial%20is%20the%20allocation%20of%20substantial%20resources%20towards%20the%20%E2%80%98loss%20and%20damage%E2%80%99%20fund%20for%20vulnerable%20countries%20as%20agreed%20at%20the%20UNFCCC%20COP27%20in%202022.%20For%20a%20rapid%2C%20just%20and%20equitable%20transition%20to%20low-carbon%20development%2C%20the%20G20%20can%20ensure%20that%20environmental%20and%20human%20rights%20safeguards%20are%20foregrounded%2C%20by%20conducting%20environment%2C%20social%20and%20cultural%20impact%20assessments%2C%20ensuring%20effective%20public%20participation%20in%20decision%20making%20and%20employing%20decentralised%2C%20nature-friendly%20and%20community-led%20solutions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20inception%20in%202008%2C%20the%20G20%20has%20engaged%20in%20discussions%20surrounding%20the%20reduction%20of%20poverty%20and%20inequality.%20Paradoxically%2C%20the%20disparities%20between%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20particularly%20Least%20Developed%20Countries%20(LDCs)%20and%20the%20Global%20North%20have%20not%20only%20endured%20but%20have%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20widened.%20Despite%20the%20existence%20of%20common%20frameworks%20and%20allocations%20of%20Special%20Drawing%20Rights%20(SDRs)%2C%20the%20aid%20provided%20to%20least%20developed%20countries%20remains%20insufficient%20to%20say%20the%20least.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%20their%20debt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Ff4b04f39-8b9d-463d-8e95-ebb0d1514e21%5C%22%3Eburden%20of%20these%20countries%20has%20increased%20significantly%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20pandemic.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20sphere%20of%20trade%2C%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organisation%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcovid-19-crisis-wto-intellectual-property-vaccine-public-health%5C%22%3E%20inability%20to%20waive%20patent%20rights%20obstructs%20the%20access%20to%20critical%20COVID-19%20medications%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20exacerbates%20vaccine%20inequality.%20G20%20leaders%20can%20address%20the%20urgent%20economic%20issues%20such%20as%20global%20taxation%20by%20securing%20clear%20commitments%20on%20tax%20heavens%2C%20tax%20avoidance%2C%20commonly%20agreeing%20to%20a%20progressive%20taxation%20regime%20and%20reshape%20the%20international%20financial%20architecture%2C%20guided%20by%20principles%20of%20global%20equality%20and%20justice.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20in%20a%20summit%20where%20two%20hefty%20powers%2C%20Russia%20and%20China%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20not%20going%20to%20be%20represented%20by%20their%20heads%20of%20state%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg20-leader-dropouts-preemptive%5C%22%3Ethereby%20already%20weakening%20prospects%20for%20any%20significant%20agreement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20may%20literally%20end%20up%20as%20a%20year-long%20preparation%20for%20the%20host%20country%E2%80%99s%20perception%20building%20in%20the%20country%20and%20globally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20this%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20story%20of%20India%2C%20which%20has%20been%20calling%20itself%20the%20%E2%80%98mother%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99%20and%20promising%20to%20voice%20the%20%E2%80%98leadership%20of%20the%20Global%20South%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Vishwaguru%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20this%20is%20happening%20at%20a%20time%20where%20there%20is%20ongoing%20rampant%20abuse%20of%20human%20rights%2C%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20religious%20freedom%2C%20relentless%20attack%20on%20civil%20society%20through%20a%20plethora%20of%20regulatory%20and%20punitive%20mechanisms%2C%20long%20incarceration%20of%20political%20prisoners%20without%20any%20trial%20for%20years%2C%20a%20virtual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fmanipur-epidemics-may-break-out-in-relief-camps-if-urgent-measures-not-taken-warn-doctors%5C%22%3Ecivil%20war%20going%20on%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20for%20about%20four%20months%20now%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20any%20accountability%20being%20fixed%20whatsoever%2C%20and%20direct%20state-backed%20patronage%20to%20fake%20propaganda%20and%20hate%20speech%20directed%20against%20religious%20minorities%20all%20over%20the%20country%2C%20particularly%20Muslims%20and%20Christians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20G20%20has%20been%20touted%20as%20the%20first%20one%20to%20bring%20such%20an%20important%20event%20to%20the%20people%20directly.%20Looking%20at%20the%20unlimited%20glittering%20G%2020%20logos%20and%20light%20and%20sound%20shows%20across%20India%20highlighting%20the%20same%2C%20one%20may%20be%20tempted%20to%20believe%20the%20same.%20However%2C%20we%20also%20know%20how%20scores%20of%20slums%20have%20been%20demolished%20or%20barricaded%20behind%20the%20gilded%20facades%20to%20make%20the%20cities%20look%20better%20before%20the%20visiting%20delegates.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20week%2C%20over%20300%20civil%20society%20delegates%20from%20across%20the%20country%20(and%20several%20representatives%20joining%20online%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world)%20met%20physically%20inside%20the%20Constitution%20Club%20in%20New%20Delhi%20as%20part%20of%20a%20People%E2%80%99s%20Assembly%20to%20articulate%20people%E2%80%99s%20expectations%20from%20the%20upcoming%20summit.%20And%20they%20were%20accompanied%20by%20scores%20of%20policemen%20of%20different%20hues%20and%20colours%2C%20recording%20each%20session%20and%20scanning%20faces%20of%20the%20speakers%20during%20those%20two%20days%2C%20a%20testimony%20to%20how%20robust%20our%20democracy%20is%20today.%20A%20week%20before%20that%20another%20gathering%20of%20civil%20society%20organisations%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe20-delhi-police-jairam-ramesh-leaders%5C%22%3Ewas%20stopped%20mid-way%20by%20the%20police%20over%20completely%20inexcusable%20excuses%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20there%20is%20a%20larger%20media%20silence%20all%20around%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDemocracy%20thrives%20only%20when%20unburdened%20by%20the%20weight%20of%20repression.%20The%20pursuit%20of%20sustainable%20development%20necessitates%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20flourishing%20civil%20society%20and%20a%20resilient%20democracy.%20These%20cornerstones%20are%20pivotal%20in%20advancing%20equitable%20progress%20and%20ensuring%20that%20the%20aspirations%20of%20all%20citizens%20are%20honoured.%20If%20G20%20leaders%20have%20the%20desire%20and%20will%20to%20change%20the%20course%20of%20the%20world%20towards%20betterment%2C%20its%20current%20president%20and%20the%20summit%20will%20have%20to%20show%20the%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EAvinash%20Kumar%2C%20Annie%20Namala%20and%20Vidya%20Dinker%20are%20the%20India%20coordinators%20of%20People%E2%80%99s%2020%2C%20a%20global%20civil%20society%20platform%20engaging%20with%20the%20G20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693987472000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06132900%2FF4b-BzwWoAADwXC.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhype-alone-cannot-sustain-the-g20-and-indias-presidency%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20look%20at%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20world%20right%20now%2C%20and%20then%20at%20India%2C%20shows%20that%20cornerstones%20pivotal%20in%20advancing%20equitable%20progress%20and%20ensuring%20that%20the%20aspirations%20of%20all%20citizens%20are%20honoured%20have%20been%20ignored.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhype-alone-cannot-sustain-the-g20-and-indias-presidency%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Dream%20Girl%202'%20crosses%20Rs%20100%20worldwide%20gross%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693987423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http