thern-ireland-12955779%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Started%20For%20My%20Daughter%E2%80%99%3A%20Assam%20Woman%E2%80%99s%20Vermicompost%20Biz%20Earns%20Her%20Rs%203.5%20Lakh%2FMonth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20was%202008.%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Kanika%20Talukdar%20was%20abound%20with%20happiness%20as%20her%20daughter%20was%20born%20after%20three%20years%20of%20her%20marriage.%20But%20this%20happiness%20could%20not%20last%20long%20because%20soon%20after%2C%20she%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20a%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%20was%20down%20with%20a%20fever%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20We%20found%20out%20that%20he%20had%20malaria.%20The%20local%20doctor%20referred%20him%20to%20a%20Guwahati%20hospital%20for%20treatment.%20Along%20with%20my%20father%2C%20he%20left%20for%20the%20city%20for%20his%20treatment%2C%20but%20soon%20we%20got%20the%20news%20that%20he%20was%20no%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Borjhar%20village%20resident%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20was%20very%20small.%20While%20we%20were%20grieving%20the%20death%20of%20my%20husband%2C%20her%20entire%20future%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20was%20in%20front%20of%20me.%20My%20parents%20brought%20me%20back%20home%20from%20my%20in-laws%E2%80%99.%20I%20thought%20of%20working%20as%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20an%20unwanted%20%3Cem%3Ebojh%20%3C%2Fem%3E(burden)%20for%20my%20elderly%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20encouraged%20Kanika%20to%20embark%20on%20a%20journey%20towards%20self-empowerment.%20Today%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20runs%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F249941%2Fhow-to-vermicompost-earn-revenue-sana-khan-sj-organics-earthworms-uttar-pradesh-sustainability-c24%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evermicompost%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20earns%20her%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20monthly.%3