litres%20of%20cold-pressed%20oils%20in%20three%20categories%20%E2%80%93%20groundnut%2C%20sesame%2C%20and%20coconut%20oil.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20nobody%20in%20my%20family%20has%20any%20history%20of%20high%20cholesterol%20levels%2C%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20feed%20my%20husband%20and%20son%20food%20cooked%20in%20refined%20oils%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2039-year-old%20software%20engineer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Gramiyaa%2C%20the%20trio%20clocks%20a%20monthly%20revenue%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%20Yaseen%20says%2050%20percent%20of%20the%20revenue%20comes%20from%20exports%20to%20countries%20like%20the%20USA%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sibi%2C%20the%20business%20is%20a%20win-win%20situation.%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20we%20have%20very%20happy%20customers.%20Seventy-five%20percent%20of%20our%20customers%20regularly%20repeat%20their%20orders.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20pursue%20my%20passion%20and%20do%20what%20I%20like.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20replicate%20the%20entire%20processing%20units%20the%20way%20my%20grandfather%20used%20to%20do.%20Unfortunately%2C%20he%20is%20not%20there%20with%20us%2C%20but%20he%20would%20have%20been%20happy%20to%20see%20that%20we%20are%20able%20to%20take%20these%20oils%20to%20so%20many%20kitchens%20like%20once%20he%20did%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ijfans.org%2Fuploads%2Fpaper%2F69c6e340b4e8890a7413d12d4fd55881.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20review%20on%20wood%20pressed%20edible%20oils%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20by%20ACS%20College%2C%20Maharashtra%20in%20the%20International%20Journal%20of%20Food%20and%20Nutritional%20Sciences%20in%20December%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C