%20of%20land.%20So%20Gurwinder%20planted%20the%20bulbs%2C%20and%20after%2090%20days%2C%20they%20started%20to%20bloom.%20He%20sold%20the%20first%20batch%20in%20the%20local%20markets%20and%20earned%20around%20Rs%203%20per%20spike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Holland%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259655%2Fyoutube-business-ideas-women-entrepreneur-udhampur-jammu-kashmir%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egladiolus%20flowers%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20one%20of%20the%20most%20widely%20used%20ornamental%20flowers%20across%20the%20world.%20With%20a%20longer%20shelf-life%20of%20seven%20days%2C%20these%20flowers%20are%20an%20economical%20agri-product%20for%20farmers.%20Hence%2C%20encouraged%20by%20the%20successful%20experiment%20and%20potential%20returns%2C%20he%20expanded%20the%20area%20under%20flower%20cultivation%20to%20one%20acre%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20he%20introduced%20other%20varieties%20of%20flowers%20from%20countries%20like%20Europe%20and%20Israel%2C%20gradually%20expanding%20the%20flower%20cultivation%20to%2022%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20flower%20farming%20with%20machines%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Gurwinder%20found%20happiness%20in%20flower%20farming%2C%20it%20came%20with%20its%20own%20set%20of%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CGladiolus%20flower%20bulbs%20resemble%20onions.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20we%20planted%20these%20bulbs%20by%20hand%20in%20beds%2C%20ensuring%20the%20pointed%20end%20faced%20upwards.%20This%20was%20a%20slow%20and%20labour-intensive%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgurwinder-singh-2-1693544473.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gurwinder%20