e%20of%20the%20incredible%20alignment%20of%20thoughts%2C%20among%20other%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20thanks%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chaithanya.%20The%20trio%20was%20discussing%20the%20unfairness%20of%20the%20situation%20%E2%80%94%20how%20abled%20students%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20continuing%20their%20schooling%20online%20while%20students%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F145157%2Fahmedabad-ngo-proves-deaf-blindedness-doesnt-hinder-learning%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20denied%20this%20basic%20right.%20They%20figured%20that%20this%20discrimination%20extended%20beyond%20the%20classroom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20if%20we%20were%20to%20start%20a%20platform%20that%20enabled%20hearing%20disabled%20people%20to%20access%20equal%20opportunities%20in%20terms%20of%20jobs%2C%20skillset%20training%20and%20more%3F%E2%80%9D%20they%20thought.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20where%20it%20all%20started%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaithanya%20shares.%20And%20there%20was%20no%20looking%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EYunikee%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20actual%20word%20(in%20Telugu)%20that%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98I%20exist.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20ignore%20me.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20The%20reason%20for%20this%20stark%20reminder%20is%20that%2C%20unlike%20people%20of%20other%20disabilities%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F110922%2Fdeaflympics-deaf-athletes-2017%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeaf%20persons%3C%2Fa%3E%20cannot%20be%20identified%20unless%20one%20speaks%20to%20them%2C%20says%20Chaithanya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20Yunikee%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20bring%20an%20identity%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20trio%20dived%20de