e%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20after%20graduating%2C%20she%20started%20an%20NGO%20in%20memory%20of%20her%20father%20%E2%80%94%20Shaheed%20Ramashray%20Welfare%20Society%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20aim%20to%20help%20victims%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20and%20domestic%20violence%20get%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NGO%20was%20my%20way%20of%20paying%20tribute%20to%20my%20father%20and%20mother.%20These%20two%20strong%20individuals%20have%20been%20a%20massive%20inspiration%20for%20me%20in%20their%20unique%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20welfare%20society%20works%20with%20victims%20of%20sexual%20and%20physical%20abuse%20and%20gives%20them%20free%20legal%20help.%20Besides%2C%20Devanshi%20also%20gives%20free%20counselling%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9CGetting%20proper%20counselling%20and%20knowing%20the%20next%20steps%20is%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20healing%20after%20abuse.%20The%20people%20who%20come%20to%20me%20are%20usually%20very%20scared%20and%20unsure%20of%20what%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20volunteers%20and%20I%20help%20them%20gain%20their%20lost%20confidence%20and%20also%20help%20them%20legally%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way.%20The%20justice%20system%20is%20not%20as%20efficient%20as%20we%20would%20like%20it%20to%20be%2C%20but%20the%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20we%20take%20the%20first%20step%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevanshi%20accompanies%20the%20victims%20to%20the%20police%20station%2C%20court%2C%20and%20wherever%20else%20is%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NGO%20in%20Bareilly%20has%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20and%20many%20people%20reach%20out%20to%20us%20if%20they%20are%20going%20through%20something%20or%20if%20they%20know%20someone%20who%20is.%20I%20have%20also%20openly%20talked%20about%20my%20trauma%20on%20social%20media%20so%20that%20more%20women%20speak%20up.%20This%20has%20helped%20and%20I%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20requests%20for%20